title: Nyasachwa Man Malo
verse1:
Nyasachwa man malo, Wuon teko duto,
Onge teko moro mak tekone adier,
Onge ng'ato moro miporo go Nyasaye, 
En Ruodh ruodhi, be Nyasach nyiseche
verse2:
Hera mar Nyasachwa, hera adieri,
En nooro Yesu nikech noherowa,
Ne Yesu othonwa mondo kik walal ngang',
To wanahere kak'owinjore.

title: WAPAKI, NYASAYE
verse1:
Wapaki, Nyasaye, In miherowa ngang'!
Nioro Wuodi mond' othonwa e yath.
verse2:
Wapaki, Nyasaye, nikech Roho Maler
Osefwenyonwa hera mar Jawarwa.
verse3:
Pak duto obed ni Nyarombo Nyasaye, 
Ma noting'o kethwa, rembe nochwernwa.
verse4:
Pak duto obed ni Nyasaye, Wuon ng'wono,
Ma noresowa kendo oritowa.
refrain:
Alleluya! Wanapaki; Alleluya! Amin.
Alleluya! Wanapaki; Igwedhawa koro.

title: Duong' obed Ni Wuonwa
verse1:
Duong' obed ni wuonwa kuom gi motimo;
Nikech nohero piny,mochiwa Wuode
Ma notho e yath mondo oluok richo,
Mondo ng'a moyie kuome oyud ngima.
verse2:
Ruoth Yesu noseng'iewowa gi rembe
Nyasaye osingo ni jo moyie kuome
Kinde ma giruako Yesu e chunygi
E ma enowenigie kethgi duto.

3.	
Osetimo tichne madongo ni piny,
Wamor moloyo kuom puonj yesu Ruodhwa;
Wanamor moloyo gi chunywa duto,
Ka waneno wang' Yesu ma Jawarwa.
refrain:
Wapak Ruoth,wapak Ruoth,piny mond' Owinj dwonde;
Wapak Ruoth,wapak Ruoth,Mondo ji Duto mor,
Biuru ni Wuonwa kuom Yesu wuode,
Mondo wapake kuom gik mosetimo.

verse3:

title: To Pakuru Ruoth
Wuonwa Wabironi
verse3:
Ng'wononi imiwa,magi chutho;
Chunywa mond' iriti, ka wan e wuoth.
Telnwa, wakwayoi, nyaka watiek wuodhwa,
Nyaka wadonj polo mar dak kodi.
refrain:
Wuonwa wabironi,wan to wanyap;
Kik iwewa kendwa;Wuonwa,winjwa.

title: Nyasaye Indi Nikonywa
verse1:
Nyasaye indi nikonyowa,
In tekowa mak rum;
Waluor ang'o tiritowa,
Ma nyaka piny ogik.
verse2:
Chon ji maler nogenoi
Niritogi mang'won;
To ng'wononi mak lokore
Omiyo wageni.
verse3:
Kane pok ichweyo piny ni
Ne gimoro onge;
To ne Intie Nyasaye maler,
Intie ma nyaka chieng'
verse4:
To gik moko duto mag piny
Gikadho a kadha;
To gir polo ma ok lal ngang'
Gir polo wanayier.
verse5:
Nyasaye indi nikonyowa,
In tekowa mak rum;
Walu bang'i pile pile,
Nyasaye ma Jakonywa.

title: Winji Yuakna Inyisa Ngwononi
verse1:
Winji yuakna, inyisa n'ononi, 
In Jakonya, bina; Chunya motur ogombo bironi, 
In Jakonya, bina.
verse2:
Aonge kara, kata kar konyruok. 
In Jakonya, bina; Wan' man'on miya bedo gi ler,
In Jakonya, bina.
verse3:
An kenda ka, to tienda ol e yo, 
In Jakonya, bina; An'yoi, mon'ayud mor kuomi, 
In Jakonya, bina.
verse4:
In ok nidag jalo ma chunye tur, 
In Jakonya, bina; Winj alamna, 
Kendo iwinj yuakna, In Jakonya, bina.

title: Jachwechna Gi Ruodha
Kristo In Wuon Ng'wono Duto
verse1:
Kristo, In Wuon ng'wono duto,
Puonj chunya mond' opaki;
Gwethni ma ayudo pile
Miyo chunya mor kuomi
Puonj heroi adieri,
Mond' aluwi kwonde tee;
Muchi mondo dak e chunya,
Miya genoi pile.
verse2:
An apaki, in Jakonya
In mitelona pile;
An kaluwo bang'i pile
Nachopi thurwa gi kuwe
Yandi Yesu to nodwara'
Ka nabayo yo marach;
Rembe nochwer mond' owara,
Noresa e kethona.
verse3:
An to, an jagope chutho
Kuom ng'wono motimona;
Hera mari mond' otweya
Abed nga'ti chutho, Ruoth.
Piny to kik oywaya kendo,
Asik kuomi,yaye Jakonya;
Achiwoni chunya koro,
Obed mari nyaka chieng.

title: Yesu Isesingo
verse3:
Yesu,konywa mondo wapaki maber,
Bedi kuom alamwa ma walami go.
Mond itegnwa  yiewa,kijiwo chunywa;
Pong chunywa gi hera, menynwa wang'yorwa
refrain:
Yesu, bi igwedhwa, ka waling'kae
Yesu, bi igwedhwa, bed butwa pile.

title: Ji Duto Mondo Wer Wendni
verse1:
Ji duto mondo wer wendni:
Denduru nying Yesu Ruodhwa!
Nyisuru duong' Nyasaye Ruodhwa
Denduru nying Yesu Ruodhwa.
verse2:
Otieko luorowa duto;
Denduru nying Yesu Ruodhwa!.
Oketho teko mar Satan,
Denduru nying Yesu Ruodhwa!.
refrain:
Denduru nyinge, Denduru nyinge,
Nying Ruodhwa obedi gi pak.
Denduru nyinge, Denduru nyinge,
Denduru nying Yesu Ruodhwa!.

title: Paki Nyasaye Mogwethowa
verse1:
Paki Nyasaye mogwethowa,
Kuom hera maduongʼ ma opak;
Paki Nyasaye ma Ruodhwa,
Nikech ogwedhi pile.
verse2:
Puonjwa mondo wawinjre,
We wach maricho duto;
Kelwa e wangʼ Nyasaye,
E piny gi e polo bende.
verse3:
Kik waweyone winjruok,
Kik wayudre mor mar piny;
Kik wadwar moloya,
Kik waneg hera mar Ruoth.
refrain:
Paki Nyasaye mogwethowa,
Paki Nyasaye maber;

title: Nyasacha, Mond' Awuoth Kodi
Wuo Gi Chunya , Ruoth Yesu
verse1:
Wuo gi chunya, ruoth Yesu, Wuona gi dwol mamuol,
Kiwachona gi ng'wono,"Ok idong' kendi ngang,"
Yaw chunya mond' opaki kamor kuomi chutho
Mi chunya mond' opaki kamor kuomi chutho.

title: Ruoth Maler, Adwari Pile
verse2:
Chuny mamuol mondo imiya; Richo osekethoa;
Puonja mondo ang'e yomna, An akwayi tekoni.
verse3:
Ok naluor kitaya pile; To kenda nagora piny;
Wuoth koda,yaye Jokonya, In lerna, In ngimana.
verse4:
Kata gi manade biro, kata mor, kata kuyo,
Chunya pod otwere kuomi, In Jakonya saa duto

title: Kristo, Ok An
verse3:
Kristo, kende, kik  agomb ng'ato moro
Kristo, kende, to kik chunya ting're
Kristo, kende, kik apakra gi berna,
Kristo, kende, ni mond' agur ringra.

title: Yesu Mond Itawa Pile
verse1:
Yesu, mond' itawa pile, wadwaro mond' iritwa;
Gi chiembi mamit yieng' chunywa, Yienwa bedo e kwedhi,
Yesu Kristo, Yesu Kristo, Iseng'iewowa, wan jogi.
Yesu Kristo, Yesu Kristo, Iseng'iewowa, wan jogi.
verse4:
Konywa mondo watim maber, Mi watim gi midwaro;
Ruoth maler, Jawarwa kende, Pong' chunywa gi herani.
Yesu Kristo, Yesu Kristo Mond' iherwa mosiko.
Yesu Kristo, Yesu Kristo Mond' iherwa mosiko.

title: Ka Ma Yesu Chon Notho E Yath
Nyasachwa En E Lwandawa
verse1:
Nyasachwa En e Lwandawa,
En Lwandawa mogen'wa;
Jakony e chandruokwa duto,
Mobedo machiegni chutho.
verse2:
Kata wach bet nade kodwa,
En Lwandawa mogen'wa;
Wan'yo kaka En Jakony,
Mobedo machiegni chutho.
verse3:
Gotieno kata godiechien'
En Lwandawa mogen'wa;
Kamano ok wanaluor ngan'
Nikech En machiegni kodwa.
verse4:
Nyasachwa e makonyowa,
En Lwandawa mogen'wa;
Ndalo duto Entie kodwa,
Obedo machiegni chutho.

title: Adwaro Ket kod Yesu
verse1:
Adwaro Ket kod Yesu; Ruodha mon'odag koda, 
Pon'chunya gi herane, Abed man'on kaka En. 
Adwaro ket kod Yesu kawuotho e pinyni ka; 
Oket Muche e chunya, Ruodha mon'odag koda.

title: Kik Ibarna,Yaye Jakonya
verse1:
Kik ibarna, yaye Jakonya, Winji yuak mara; 
In Kiluongo jo mamagi, Mon'iluonga be.
verse2:
An kaparo n'ono mari chunya yudo kuwe; 
Ka agoni chonga piny ka, Jawarna, Konya.
verse3:
An ageno nyingi kende, Adwaro neni; 
Changi chunya moseketho, Wara gi rembi.
verse4:
Miwaso ohewa kodi, To agombi ng'g; 
Ere n' maromo kodi E piny gi polo?

title: Aheri , Aheri
Jawarna To Ni Yesu
verse1:
Jawarna to ni Yesu, En morna gi wenda;
Ohoyoa gi wachne, ka chunya okuyo.
verse2:
Yesu ni n' mageno, ndalo duto Entie;
Ka piny otimo mudho, Lerne omenyoa.
verse3:
Agenoi Jawarna, Osiep mageno chuth;
Yandi ahero bayo, koro abet buti.
verse4:
In e wenda gi morna, E pinyni mar chandruok;
In e wenda gi morna, kadonjo e polo.

title: In E Ngimana Mochwere
verse1:
In e ngimana mochwere moloyo duto me piny,
E wuodha duto me piny ka, Jawaryie awuoth kodi
Kodi Ruoth,kodi Ruoth, Kodi Ruoth,kodi Ruoth;
E wuodha duto me piny ka, Jawar yie awuoth kodi.
verse2:
Ok alem ne mor mar pinyni, ok alem mond' ayud dwong'
Nati gi mor kat' e chandruok, Yie mondo awuoth kodi.
Kodi Ruoth,kodi Ruoth, Kodi Ruoth,kodi Ruoth
Nati gi mor kat' e chandruok, Yie mondo awuoth kodi.
verse3:
Telna e pinyni mar mudho ting'a mondo alo piny
Eka mondo adonj kodi e ngima ma ok norum.
Kodi Ruoth,kodi Ruoth, Kodi Ruoth,kodi Ruoth;
Eka mondo adonj kodi e ngima ma ok norum.

title: Ji Duto Te Mondo Giwer
verse1:
Ji duto te mondo giwer
Ka gipako Jawar'ka gipako Jawar
Gipak duong' mar Ruoth Naysachwa
Kod ng'uonone maduong'.
verse2:
Ruodha maduong' gi Nyasachwa
Konya mondo ahul,konya mondo ahul
Duong mar nying Ruoth gi Jawarna
E kuonde duto te.
verse3:
Yesu en nying' makelo mor
Ogolo kuyowa, Ogolo kuyowa,
En wer mamit ni jaricho
En ngimana kod kuwe.
verse4:
Oketho teko mar richo
Ogonyo jomotwe,ogonyo jomotwe
Rembe nyalo luoko richo
Rembeno nochwerna.

title: To En Ng'a Man e kund dhok
verse1:
To en ng'a man e kund dhok
Ma jokwath olamo cha?
verse2:
To en nga'e thim kucha
Ma Satan ne otemo?
verse3:
To en ng'a mayuak e liel
Kama Lazaro oninde
verse4:
To en ng'a ma ji pako
Nikech weche mag ng'wono?
verse5:
To en ng'a mathiedho ji
Ma noyawo wang' muofuni?
refrain:
En e Ruoth! To en Jawarwa
En e Ruoth! Moloyo duto
Wanagone chongwa piny
Pakeuru Yesu Ruoth

title: Nying' Mamit E Piny Gi Polo
verse1:
Nying' mamit e piny gi polo,
Nying' Yesu Ruodha;
An alamo nying' Yesu,
Nying' Yesu Ruodha.
verse2:
Nying' Yesu ma yom e dhogwa,
Nying' Yesu Ruodha;
Ma yudore gi hera,
Nying' Yesu Ruodha.
verse3:
Nying' Yesu ruoth gi jachungi,
Nying' Yesu Ruodha;
Nying' Yesu, jawarwa,
Nying' Yesu Ruodha.
verse4:
Nying' Yesu mar tho kod chwer,
Nying' Yesu Ruodha;
Nying' Yesu mar luor,
Nying' Yesu Ruodha.
refrain:
Nying' Yesu! Nying' Yesu!
Nying' Yesu! Nying' Yesu!
Nying' Yesu, jawarwa,
Nying' Yesu Ruodha.

title: Yesu Jakwath Moheroa
verse1:
Yesu Jakwath Moheroa, Okecha ndalo duto.
An ok achand gimoro ka, Owauotho koda nyaka chieng'
verse2:
Naweyo yo , nalal marach, To En Owuon nodwara;
Noting'a mos e goke to Nomor kotera dalane,
verse3:
Kar lek mamit, kar pi mang'ich, Otera kanyo pile;
Okwayoa, orita, Yesu Jakwath mang'won adier.
verse4:
Ka tho nitie adagi luer KA Yesu bedo koda;
Ohoyoa,osiroa, En bende e motelona.
verse5:
Opedho  mesa nyima ka, Otimo sap misango;
Omiya mor gi cham maler, Remb Yesu miyo chunya yom.

title: Apaka Hera Nyasaye Wuora
verse1:
Apako hera Nyasaye Wuora mochiwona Rohone,
Molokona kuyona bedo mor koweyo na richona;
Kata mudho olil manade, osesingo nobed buta
Omiya ler marieny e mudho, Kendo ber e kar richo.
verse2:
Awero hera  mar Jawarna manotho e yath ni an
Ni mondo kobedo e chunya nogonya kuom twech duto;
Obiro waro jomaricho obiro konyo chuny mool,
Omiya nor e saa mar kuyo kendo ber e kar richo.
verse3:
Apako ber mar wach injili monyisa weche mamit,
Nomiya mor mar nyiso lerna , ka manade ma antie,
Orwaka gi law mar herane ka chunya opong' gi luoro
Omiya ler marieny e mudho kendo ber e kar richo.
refrain:
Omiya mor....E saa mar kuyo
Ogolona luoro mar tho
Omiya ler marieny e mudho
Kendo ber  kar richo

title: Duto Paki, Ruoth Polo
Koro Ka Wachokore
verse1:
Koro ka wachokore
Ni mondo wahing Yesu,
Wanapar Yesu Kristo,
Wanayiee gi chunywa;
Koro wahing Yesu,
Ma notho e Kalwari.
verse2:
Ka wachamo makate ni,
Kwamadho kikombe ni,
Wanahing ringre Jawar,
Ma nogur e yath ni wan;
Wanahing  remb Ruoth Yesu,
Ma nochwere e Kalwari
verse3:
Nyasachwa ,ornwa Muchi,
Mondo donji e chunywa;
Koro wahing Wuodi,
Kaka En notho niji,
Kaka rembe nochwernwa,
Ka notho e Kalwari.

title: Wuonwa, Gonywa Gi Gweth Mari
verse1:
Wuonwa , gonywa gi gweth mari,
Pong? chunywa gi mor gi kuwe;
Miwa duto herruok mari,
Kethowa bende iwe.

Miwa geno,miwa geno,
Ka wawuotho e pinyini.
verse2:
Wachiwo  pak gi mor bende,
Kuom weche mioronwa;
Ka wamako chikni chutho
Wanabed e herani.

Konywa timo, Konywa timo,
Gi kinda nyaka ibi.
verse3:
Ka wawuotho e piny kae,
Ber wati ni In kende;
Konywa ka walu e yori,
Kik wajogi, kik wawe.

Bedi kodwa, bedi kodwa,
Ka wawuok, bende kwake.

title: Nyasaye Wachungo Ka Wawer
verse1:
Nyasaye wachungo ka wawer kae
Ni mondo igwedhwa ka pok kwadhi
Wadwaro lami, ka wan nyimi ka
Ka wagochongwa lamoi gi kuwe.
verse2:
Miwa kuwe mari ka wadhi koro
Chako gi tieko inibed kodwa
Dhowa moselami e wich kuot
verse4:
Koro Nyasaye waparoi tinde,
Ka koro wasewinjo wach mamit;
Konywa ni mondo wamak wecheni,
Kik Satan mawa kata wach achiel.

title: Paruru Nying Yesu Koro
verse1:
Paruru nying Yesu koro, Un jopiny machandore;
En nomiu doko mamor, Paruru nyinge koro.

	Nyinge ber..moloyo.
	Nyingeno wagen ka;
	Nyinge ber..moloyo.
	(Nyinge ber ,Ober moloyo)
	Nyingeno wageno ka.
verse2:
Paruru nying Yesu pile, Enogeng'nu maricho;
Ka orwakowa gi ng'uono, Paruru nying Yesu Ruoth.
verse3:
Paruru Yeus koro, E manyalo konyou;
Ka orwakowa gi ng'uono, Paruru nying Yesu Yesu Ruoth.
verse4:
En Ruoth ruothi, wanadende Ka wagone chonge piny,
Kucha e pinyruoth mar polo, Ka wuodhwa me piny rumo.

title: Ruoth Yesu ,Nithona
verse2:
Aheri nikech nihera mokwongo,
Niting'o richona e yadh Kalwari;
Nichandori malit nikech richona
Koro, Yesu Ruodha, aheri adier.
verse4:
Eka kwadak kodi e dala Nyasaye,
E pinyruoth manyienno nadendi pile.
Kosidhna osimbo napaki kawer;
Koro, Yesu Ruodha, aheri adier.

title: Yesu In Miheroa
verse3:
Yo machielo ok adwar, In Iwuon e wang'yora,
Kik idaga, kik iling', Sira ,hoya,ngwonona.
Ee,Jakony, agenoi,Tekoni ichiwona;
Chungi buta nyaka chieng', Demba, rita kik alal.
verse4:
Yesu, miya ng'wononi, golna richo duto te,
Hombo to ahomboi, Luoka ,guda,konya chuth,
Bedi koda nyaka chieng', Nyisa tich michikoa;
Dag e chunya , kik ia, Ndalo duto nyaka chieng'.

title: Anawer Hera Yesu
verse1:
Anawer hera Yesu, Anawer koheroa.
Noweyo polo malo. Nosetho e Kalwari.

Anawer hera Yesu, Anapake gi chunya
Nosetho e Kalwari. Anawer koheroa.
verse2:
Anwer ng'wono Yesu, Anawer kong'wonona;
Enowena kethona, Enoyie ni an mare.
verse3:
Yesu, donji e chunya, In Jakonya pile ka;
Konya timo tim maber, Kendo konya hero In.
verse4:
Tim maber onge kuoma; Awuoro kak' ihera;
Ruodha, kaw chunya koro, Obed mari nyaka chieng'.

title: Nitie Wer Mamit E Dhoga
verse1:
Nitie wer mamit e dhoga, Nikech osewara,
Kuom Jawarna, Yesu, Ruodha, Nikech osewara.
verse2:
Kristo En ng'a moyieng'no chuny, Nikech osewara
Adwaro timo dwarone Nikech osewara.
verse3:
Adwaro bed janenone,Nikech osewara;
Aonge kiawa e chunya, Nikech osewara.
verse4:
Olosona kar bet malo, Nikech osewara;
Nadag kanyo ma nyaka chieng', Nikech osewara.

title: Alleluia Ruoth Nochier
verse1:
E Kalwari Jawar notho
E kanyono Jawar nogur
E wi Yadhno Rembe nochwer
Kendo nokawo chandruok na.
verse2:
E dier Luanda polo duto
Chuny Jawarna nochot kanyo
Law ma noyiech nosiemo yo
Madhi e mor ma ok norum.
verse3:
O Yesu Ruoth nobed nade!
Nichiwo ngimani ni an
Mar ting'o chuat Msalaba
E saa malich E Kalwari.
refrain:
E Kalwari kanyo molil
Kama remb Yesu nochwerna
E Kalwari manogwedhi
Kanyo Jawarna nothona.

title: E Kalwari Jawar Notho
verse1:
E Kalwari Jawar notho
E kanyono Jawar nogur
E wi yadhno Rembe nochwer
Kendo nokawo chandruok na.
verse2:
E dier Luanda polo dudo
Chuny Jawarna nochot kanyo
Law ma noyiech nosiemo yo
Madhi e mor ma ok norum
verse3:
O Yesu Ruoth nobed nade!
Nichiwo ngimani ni an
Mar ting'o chuat Msalaba
E saa malach E Kalwari
refrain:
E Kalwari kanyo molil
Kama remb Yesu nochwerna
E Kalwari manogwedhi
Kanyo Jawarna nothona.

title: Hera Ma Yesu Hera Go Ma Nomiyo Otho E Yath
verse1:
Hera ma Yesu hera go nomiyo otho e yath
Mondo owena richona Oloyo lep wacho.
	
Hera ne oloyo lep wacho, Hera ne oloyo lep wacho
Hera ma Yesu herago;oloyo lep wacho.
verse2:
Kuyo maduong' manoyudo g'osimb kudho na nosidhne
Mond' ayud ngima nyaka chieng' oloyo lep wacho.
verse3:
Kuwe maduong' ma an go kuome en masayona nyim
Nyasaye; Rembe maler mano chwerna oloyo lep wacho.
verse4:
Mor mayudo ka en buta, Kanindo anto ok naluor
Genona kuome duong' chutho oloyo lep wacho.

title: Adwaro Ng'eyo Wach Yesu
verse3:
Ne gigure e msalaba, Mano wach modhiera ngang';
Kanyo nonwang'o masira, To noyie tho nikech wan.
Hera maduong', ee , awuoro, Mokadho hera mar ji,
Ita opowore koro, Chunya amiye chutho.

title: Ang'eyo Yesu Osewara
verse1:
Ang'eyo Yesu osewara Kuom herane gi ng'wonone;
E nengo mochulo e thone, Omiya bedo nyathine.

Osewara! Yesu owara gi rembe
Osewara! Asebet nyathine chutho.
verse2:
Amor nikech Ruoth osewara; Onge dhum ma dahul godo
Herano ma an go e chunya, Ka koro Yesu dak koda.
verse3:
Ageno neno Ruodha Yesu E duong'ne gi berne duto;
Otayo tienda e wang'yore, Oketo chikne e chunya.
verse4:
E dala maler mar Nyasachwa Osimb ngima oritoa;
Chieng moro kobiro gi duong'ne Eka nabbed kode e polo.

title: Ndalo Mamor
verse1:
Ndalo mamor, Ka Nahulo
Kak\' ageni, In Jawarna
Chunya opong gi mor chutho
Ok dak anyal mung\'o
verse2:
wasetimo winjruok kode'
An ng\'ate chuth, to En Ruodha;
An koro aluwo bang\'e
Amor nyiso ji kuomJawar
verse3:
Chunya koro oyudo kuwe
Kapadora kuom Jakonya.
To kik aweye kendo ngang\'.
Asiki kode nyaka chieng\'

title: Chunya Nigi Mor Moloyo
verse1:
Chunya nigi mor moloyo
Kating'o dwonda pako Ruoth;
To ng'a mowinjore pako
Nying Yesu Kuom hera modhiero?
verse3:
Yesu owinja kayuakne,
Oting'a malo kapodho;
E ngimana nyaka thona
Nagen hera maduong' mar Yesu.

title: Yesu Jawarwa E Bethlehem Chon.
verse1:
Yesu Jawarna e Bethlehem chon
Nonyuol e ot ka ma dhok nindoe;
E , awuoro kaka nowarowa,
Kaka nowarowa.
 
Nobiro warowa, Nobiro warowa,;
Ee, apako nyinge nikech yandi
Nobiro warowa.
verse2:
Yesu Jawrwa e Kalwari chon
Nochulo gopwa, nogonyo chunywa;
Ee, awuoro kaka notho ni wan,
Kaka notho ni wan, Nobiro tho niwan.

Nobiro tho ni wan, Nobiro tho nni wan;
Ee apako nyinge nikech yandi
Nobiro tho ni wan.
verse3:
Yesu Jawarwa nomanyowa chon,
Ka ne waruenyo , ka ne ok wayie;
Ee, awuoro kaka noluongowa.
Kaka noluongowa.

Nobiro luongowa, Nobiro luongowa
Ee,apako nyinge nikech yandi
Nobiro luongowa
verse4:
Yesu Jawarwa chieng' moro nob,
Nobi mondo om nyithinde maler;
Ee, awuoro kaka obiro ka,
Obiro omowa.

Obiro omowa, Obiro omowa;
Ee, opako nyinge t'obiro ka,
Obiro omowa

title: Yesu Kristo Oberna Ngang'
Ywaya Machiegni Kodi, Ruodha
verse2:
Ywaya machiegni kuom ng'wononi;
Onge gi ma dakel ni Jawarna,
To mana richo man e chunya
Yiena mondo ipwodha gi rembi
Yiena mondo ipwodha gi rembi.

title: Kristo Obed Misango Mar Golo Richo
verse1:
Kristo noluoko richona
En Jawar miwuoro ngang'
Ochulo nengo nikech wan
En Jawar miwuoro ngang'!
verse2:
Apake Kuom remo maler
En Jawar miwuoro ngang'
Moriwo chunya gi Nyasaye,
En Jawar miwuoro ngang'!
verse3:
Ogolo richo e chunya
En Jawar miwuoro ngang'!
Koro obed Ruoth maduong',
En Jawar miwuoro ngang'!

4.Owuotho koda yo duto,
En Jawar miwuoro ngang'!
Omiya teko mar ritruok,
En Jawar miwuoro ngang'!

    ...
refrain:
En Jawar miwuoro ngang'!
En Yesu, En Yesu
En Jawar miwuoro ngang'!
En Yesu Ruodha!

title: Jakwath Nokwayo Rombege
verse1:
Jakwath nokwayo rombege Pier ochiko gochiko,
To achiel kuomgi ne olalne Ma notimo piero apar
Adier nolal e got moro,Ne en ku mabor ma onge jakwath.
verse2:
Rombege pier ochiko gochiko Ok romi, yaye, Ruoth?
To en oruakoi gango Kuom achiel mabayo yo?
To gode be rach chutho; Kik ichandri, Ruoth kayiem nono.

title: Jawar Yesu Itelna
verse1:
Ka'apaka gingore, Inyalo kueyo yamo.
Apaka mager winji kichiko mondo gikwe.
In Jaloch maduon'mar nam, Jawar Yesu itelna.
verse2:
Ka achiegni gi chopo, ka yembe malich kudho
Edho nam mokwe maber, ka ayiengora kuomi Yie,
Awinji kiwachona, "Kik iluor anatelni."

title: Wapako Ruoth Ma Jawarwa
verse1:
Wapako Ruoth ma Jawarwa, Muche oriwowa;
To koseriwowa kama Walam gi chuny achiel.
verse2:
Ochikowa wagene ka, wabed achiel kuome;
One'wawuoth kanyakla ka wachiko yor polo.
verse3:
Ochiwo michne nijogo mageno nyinge chuth;
Wanyiso n'onone kama, kwaherore maber.
verse4:
Kwawinjore maber e piny, Kwamor kuom Yesu Ruoth,
To mor manade ma nobet kwachokore e polo.

title: Wuod Dhano Ma Ne Otho
verse1:
Ne gigure Golgotha, Tho malit Owuon noyie;
Chunya mor, nawer kama, Alleluya! En Jakonya.
verse2:
Jo maricho chon kucha, Ne gisin kode marach;
Rembe to nowarowa; Alleluya! En Jakonya.
verse3:
Yesu In nitho kama! Nyaka chien'naluwi ka;
Chunya mor, nawer kama, Alleluya! En Jakonya.

title: Awero Teko Mar Nyasaye
verse1:
Awero n'ono mar Nyasaye Mamiyowa chiemo,
Nochweyo duto gi Wachne, Noneno duto ber,
Ruoth, ka manade man'yo aneno tich mag lueti;
Polo ohulo duon'Nyasaye, Piny nyiso herane.

title: Ruoth Awinjo Wach Mar Gwethni
verse1:
Kik ikadha, yaye Nyasacha, Richo oseloyoa;
Kik iweya, yaye Jakonya, To inyisa n'ononi.
verse2:
Kik ikadha, In Wuon n'ono, Chik tienda e wan'ori;
An agombo luwi pile, Taya pile e piny ka.
verse3:
Kik ikadha, yaye Jawarna, In Wuon ngima maradier;
Muchi mondo dak e chunya, Kendo puonja wecheni.

title: Roho Mar Nyasaye Ibina
verse1:
Roho mar Nyasaye, bi kuoma; Kata ok anyal neni
To adwaro mon'ibina, Bi, ipon'chunya koro.
verse2:
An ayom, aonge teko, An akulorani, Ruoth;
Roho mar Nyasaye maler, to Mon'imiya tekoni.
verse3:
Luoka, hoya, thiedha, gwedha; Herani opon'hunya;
Konya, sira, taya pile; Gwethni mon'osik koda.

title: Muya Maler Jatendwa
Muya Maler Winj Alamwa
verse1:
Bi kaka ler! Mon'ifwenynwa Kethwa,
Kitwa maricho;
Mon'itelnwa e yor ngima,
En yor jo mabeyo.
verse2:
Bi kaka mach, ipwodh chunywa,
Kuom gik maricho duto;
Mondo wachiwre ni Ruodhwa,
Misango mangima.
verse3:
Bi kaka koth, mi igwedhwa,
Ka pod wan nyimi kae;
Dak ipon'a gi tekoni,
Kiloyo chunywa chuth.
verse4:
Kaka yamo mondo ibi,
Gi teko kaka chon cha;
Mondo warruok man kuom Yesu,
Olandre piny duto.

title: Much Nyasaye Iler Chutho
verse1:
Much Nyasaye, ahombi ngan'
Mi chunya bedo maler;
Nyaka a ndalo man'ny
Kethruok oseloyoa.
verse2:
Much Nyasaye, Jakony madier,
Dak e chunya, miya kuwe;
Gol kethruok oko chutho,
Changi chunya man gi tuo.

title: Osiep Manade En Mor Manade
verse1:
Anyalo wuotho e yorno madiny,
Ka ayiengora kuom Ruoth Yesu;
En yo maber madhiyo kar ngima
Ka iyiengori kuom Ruoth Yesu.
verse2:
Onge gimoro monego aluor
Ka ayiengora kuom Ruoth Yesu.
Ruoth nobed koda ndalo duto te,
Ka ayiengora kuom Ruoth Yesu.

title: Onge Osiep Moro Kaka Yesu
verse1:
Onge osiep man gi duon'ka Yesu,
En kende! En kende!
To chunye muol moloyo ji duto;
En kende! En kende!
verse2:
Onge saa moro mak Entie kodwa,
Ka'achiel, ka'achiel.
Kata e mudho En kodwa pile;
En kende! En kende!
verse3:
To En Osiep ma ok enowewa;
En kende! En kende!
Onge jaketh ma Yesu ojaro,
Ka'chiel, ka'chiel.
verse4:
Noherowa nyaka ne othonwa;
En kende! En kende!
Ok enojwan'nyithinde mohero,
Ka'achiel, ka'achiel.

  ....

title: Onge Osiep Moro Kaka Yesu_1
verse2:
In Jawarna, isen'ewoa, Ngimana duto mari;
Mon'anyis pakni gi duon'i Kuom kit wuodha e piny ka.
To ageno piny Ruodh polo, Ma herani non'ewona.
En e gi maparo pile Chunya mor kuomi, Ruodha.

title: Kabedo E Tiend Ruoth Yesu
Ruodha Aheri Maradier
verse1:
An'yo Intie buta, Ruoth, Moloyo ji me piny;
Kaparoi ayudo mor Moloyona mor piny.
verse2:
Iketo morni e chunya, Ma piny ok nyal golo;
Da ok abed gi herani, Kuyo dipon'chunya.
verse3:
Kwayudo mor e ngimawa Kwawuotho kodi ka,
To wanayud mor manade Kwaneni Wan'gi Wan'

title: Aseyudo Osiep Maber
verse1:
Aseyudo Osiep maber; Notho e msalaba
Ni mon'ayud ngima kuome, Ringre Owuon nomiya.
Gik moko duto ma an go, Ok maga to mag Yesu;
Chunya, ringra, giga duto Ni mag Yesu mochwere.

title: Nyasachwa Mondo Obed Kodu
verse1:
Nyasachwa mondo obed kodu, En ogen'u gi luete;
En man'on, En to noritu; Nyasachwa mondo obed kodu.
verse2:
Nyasachwa mondo obed kodu. En 'miu bet mangima,
Bende En ohoyo chunyu; Nyasachwa mondo obed kodu.
verse3:
Nyasachwa mondo obed kodu; Kata ka masich tho yudwa.
To wanere e pinyruodhe; Nyasachwa mondo obed kodu.

title: Yesu Nowara
verse1:
Yesu nopuonja hero Nyasaye; an koro adwaro puonjo jopiny,
Kata gikwero, kata giyie, Ok anamun'ngan' ok analin'
verse2:
Koro kageno Ruoth Jakonya, Yesu e berna bende e lerna;
Ka tichne rumo, ka piny ogik, Eka nobi mon'okaw joge.

title: Puonja Injili Lilo
Nyasaye Wachokore
verse1:
E nyim kom-duon'Wuonwa Walamo gi chunywa;
Kuom yie, gi geno, gi paro, Chunywa bedo achiel.
verse2:
Wariwo chandruokwa, Gi tin'a duto be;
Wajiwore kuom Nyasachwa Kwakonyore maber.

title: Puonja Wach Biblos
verse1:
Miya wach Biblos, ka chunya ohewa,
Kapon'gi luoro kuom kuyo gi keth;
Weche mamit ma noa e dho Yesu
Ginijiw chunya mon'agen Jawar.
verse2:
Miya wach Biblos mondo meny wan'ora,
Puonja kuom chwanyruok mantie e piny ka;
Lerno madieri noneg mudho duto,
Lerno manyalo menyonwa yor kuwe.
verse3:
Miya wach Biblos, tach ngima mochwere,
Tin' malo kichun'e dho liel;
Nyisa lerno morienynwa a e polo,
Otayowa e yo madhi polo.

title: Ahero Weche Mag Nyasaye
verse1:
Weche mamit monyisa ka Kaka Yesu yande otho;
Ee, notho kara ni mondo Anwan'ngima mochwere.
verse2:
Adwaro yie weche duto ma Nyasaye osewenwa ka;
Mondo agen hera Nyasaye, Mondo an bende ahere.
verse3:
Kaketho weche mag Nyasaye, Koro atieko chwanyora;
Ka chunya tek, kadagi yie, Koro asemiyo wan'.
verse4:
Weche Nyasaye gin ler mar piny, Onego kik ami wan';
To ni mondo ane lerne, Ni mondo kik achwanyora.

title: Ahero Nyiso Weche
verse2:
Ahero nyiso wachne, en wach maberna ngan'
Pile kanyiso n'to, omitna moloyo;
Ahero nyiso jogo ma pok owinjo ngan'
Kaka Yesu othonwa mon'omiwa ngima.
verse3:
Ahero poro wachne; kata jo man'ye
Aneno pod gihero winjo wach Ruoth Yesu;
Kendo e polo malo kawero wer manyien,
Napor wach kuom Jawarwa, weche mahero ngan'

73

title: Bende Nuchungi E Ndalo Chandruok
verse1:
Kichungo motegno e lwandano
Nikech Yesu en e lwandano,
Ka roho mare bende teloni
Inilo temruok gi tekone.
verse2:
Nomiyi chungo e ndalo luoro
Ka onyisi ka chandruok chiegni,
Ka apaka ger ka yembe kudho
Onge apaka ma diyuayi.
verse3:
Ok onyal pudhre kata e kar tho
Ka pige man'ch bwogo ringrewa
Ka'apaka n'ny pod nochun'matek
Ka wageno kuom Ruoth Jawarwa.
verse4:
Ka wanane ler ka piny yawore
Rangeye mag lulu ka rieny maler
Wanachun'matek kwan'yo polo
Ka chandruok kadho ma nyaka chien'

title: Adwaro Ngeyo Wach Yesu
verse1:
Wach mar Yesu apuonjora, Mondo an' gi modwaro;
Roho Maler otelona, En opuonja ndalo duto.
verse2:
Adwaro somo Wach mare, Omiya winjruok kod Ruodha;
Kawinjo dwonde e Wachne, Okonya chiko ngimana.
verse3:
Adwaro winjo kuom Yesu, Weche duto ma kuom duon'e;
Adwaro ngimano mak rum Ka Ruodh mirembe noduogi.

title: Chwoyo Ndalo Duto
verse1:
Chwoyo pinje duto, kata tek ahinya,
Yesu e mochiko mon'wadhi kode;
Wan gi kinde tinde, kik wanindi koro,
Mondo wadhiuru chwoyo wach maber.
verse2:
Kata en Satani, en mawuonda nono,
En mamayo chutho jo madagi wach;
To wachwo gi kinda, wanatim sinani,
Keyo biro chopo, wanamor maber.

title: Kony Jo Madwaro Tho
verse1:
Kata gigalore, en pod orito
Mon'oruak jogo maloko chunygi;
Un kik uchagi ngan' nyisgi kuom Yesu, 
Nowe kethgi ka giyawne chunygi.

title: Aparo Tinende Kuom Pinyno
verse1:
Kuom teko mar Jawar mon'ati ken'alem,
Mon'atim rito ka jalok ji;
Ni mondo awinj dwond Ruodha kowachona,
"Bi, idonj e morna koro."
verse2:
Nobed mor manade ka aneno wan',
Ngimana anaket e luete;
Sulwe nobedna duon'e dala dhahabu,
Ka ma nayudie gweth nyaka chien'

title: Kik Ibadhri Ni Tich
Daher Tiyo Kodi Ruodha
verse1:
Malaika marateke,Tiyoni gi n'ech;
Wagombo bedo kamano, Jotich malon'.
verse2:
Pile, pile miwa teko, Geno mana In;
Eka chien'ma Yesu wiro, Tich norum chutho.

title: Tiuru Yesu Biro
Ka Manade Ma Ruoth Luongae
verse1:
Kata nitie weche mag konyruok monego awach tinde
Kata nitie n'to moketho, Monego anyise yo;
Ruodha, In kibedo Jatenda, Ka yo bet malich nade,
Nawach wechego ma ichikoa, Dwonda nolu weche magi.
verse2:
Kata ka ok anyal tich maduon'Kaka jomoko timo,
An'yo nitie tich moro, Ruoth, Ma anyalo tiyoni.
Kamano aketora kuomi, An'yo kihera ngan'
Natim tich duto minyisa.

title: Yesu Osiep Malongo
verse3:
Anyise weche duto, Morna gi kuyona;
Anyise gik maolo chuny, Kod gigo machanda.
Onyisa gi mone'atim Ka'anyalo loyo.
Kamano watwak kode, Ruodha kod an.

title: Kaparo Yath Mar Kalwari
verse1:
Kaparo yath mar Kalwari,
Ka ma Ruodhwa Yesu notho,
Akwano mwandu ka nono,
Anego sunga mar chunya.
verse2:
Ruoth, kik iyie mon'apakra
Mak kuom tho Kristo Nyasacha;
Gik ma nono maywayoa
Achiwogi kuom remb Yesu.
verse3:
Kuom wiye, luetene, tiende,
Rembe nochwer koherowa;
Noyie malit nikech jopiny,
Notho mon'omiwa ngima.
verse4:
Da piny duto obed mara,
Dobed mich ma ok dak nyal rom;
Hera maduon'kama noyud chunya, 
Ringra, ngima duto.

title: Tiuri, Tiuru
verse1:
Tiuru, tiuru, wan jotich mag Nyasaye;
Waluuru yorno ma Ruoth ochikowa.
Weche duto ma luetewa oseyudo,
Watimgi gi teko duto te ma wan go.
verse2:
Tiuru, tiuru, kuchiwo chiemb ngima,
Gi pi ngima ni jo ma riyo oloyo;
Msalaba gi bendechwa mon'orieny ni ji,
Kwayalonigi n'ono mar Ruoth Nyasachwa.
verse3:
Tiuru, tiuri, wan duto watiyo,
Mondo pinyruodh mudho koro orum chutho;
To pinyruoth mar Kristo omedre kendo rieny.
Kwagoyo erokamano ni gweth mare.
verse4:
Tiuru, tiuri, kuom teko mar Ruodhwa;
Eka chien'giko wanayud osimb ngima.
Jo maler ginirieny kaka chien'godiechien'
Waweruru kwapako n'ono mar Ruodhwa.

title: Wan Wamor Kwatiyo Ni Ruoth Yesu
verse1:
Wan wamor kwatiyo ni Ruoth Yesu;
Wan wawuok ka chunywa yie timo
Tich manade ma Ruodhwa ochiko,
Wanatim kinda kuom tich Ruodhwa.
verse2:
Wanamor mar nyiso ji wach kuome,
Ka'ohero ji duto e piny;
Kristo, mobedo e duon'mar Wuoro,
Ochiwo gwethne kuom n'onone.
verse3:
Wabedo mamuol kwaluwo Ruodhwa,
Kwawuotho e yo motelonwa;
Jo molal wakelo ir Jawarwa,
Kwanyisogi Yesu ma Jakony.

title: Jokeyo ni Kanye
verse1:
Jokeyo ni kanye mondo tim tich
Mar kayo cham maber e piny marach?
Pand keyo en adier mar Wach Nyasaye,
To yueyo onge nyaka tich rumo.
verse4:
Biuru koro, un yawuot dhano,
Tiuru kanyakla mar choko cham;
Tiuru matek nyaka Ruoth biro,
Eka unudonji e mor mar Ruoth.

title: E Dho Wath Man Loka Nam
verse1:
E dho wath man loka nam; Pewe rieny kuno maler
Nitie duol moluongaee; nyaka aret adhi kanyo.
verse2:
Awinjo Ruoth kowacho, Un jokeyo ret uru
Nikech puothe nimabor, jopinywa we uru adhi.
verse3:
E apaka mogingore bat motin' ma neno
Ne rangeye bende oyaw kendo jomolal luonga.
verse4:
Wuonwa, minwa, nyithindwa nyaka agonu oriti
Nikech dho wath nam mabor nitie tich ma Ruoth luonga.

title: En Madhiyo Tich Gi Chandruok
verse1:
En madhiyo tich gi chandruok,
Ka otin' koth hera,
Ok ojogi kata nindo,
Nikech n'ono mar Nyasaye.
verse2:
Muya mar Nyasaye, lor kuomwa,
Rieny maler machalo chien'
Ni mondo wanyag olembe
Gi teko mar Nyarombo.
verse3:
Kik iol kuom chuoyo kodhi,
Kik ibed gi luoro ngan'
Bedi janeno madieri,
Iniyud mor kuom Ruodhi.

title: Winjuru Sigandwa Miwuoro
verse1:
Winjuru sigandwa miwuoro,
Ne wadak kuom jomo lal
To Yesu nolor gi duon'mare,
Warowa e twech malich.
verse2:
Onge malaika mad konywa
Mak mana Yesu Ruodhwa
Ne gigure ka gikwede chuth
To en achiel gi Wuongi.
verse3:
Yie mon'ichiwri ni Jawarni!
Yie ichiwri ne sani In bende nine n'ono mare,
Onyalo wari sani.

title: Nitie Luong Mobiro E Wi Apaka
verse1:
Nitie luong mabiro ewi apaka,
Kow ler kow ler
Nitie chuny mi konyo gi chuny miwaro
Kow ler kow ler.
verse2:
Wasewinjo luong mar jo Makedoni
Kow ler kow ler
Waketo misango e msalaba
Kow ler Kow ler.
verse3:
Walem ni gweth oumwa kwonde duto
Kow ler kow ler
Mondo much Kristo'andre kuonde duto,
Kow ler kow ler.
verse4:
Kik wajony mar lando tich mar herane,
Kow ler kow ler
Wachok lulu duto ni osimbewa
Kow ler kow ler.

title: Bende Ipuonj Ji Wach Nyasaye
verse1:
Bende ipuonjo ji wach Nyasaye, gokinyi ka pod wan'chien'nitie?
Bende ipuonjo ji wach Nyasaye, owadwa e saa ma chien'rieny makech.
verse2:
Bende ipuonjo ji wach Nyasaye, gotieno ka piny olin'malich?
Bende ipuonjo ji wach Nyasaye owadwa ne keyono madwon'aber.
verse3:
Bende ipuonjo ji wach Nyasaye gi yorno maji nyalo winjo?
Mon'ichok cham maber chien'keyono,
kawuono tim winjruok kod Ruoth Yesu.

title: Teche Duto Onego Liel
verse1:
Teche duto onego liel, mudho ni e piny kae;
Mudho maduon'nobed e piny ka Yesu pok obiro.
verse2:
Nindo otero ji man'ny, Gidagi wach Injili;
To wan waketo genowa kuom wach mar duogo Yesu.
verse3:
Tachwa ni wachne madieri, Ok wa nalal kwaluwe
Kata masiche lworowa, ToYesu ok nowewa.
verse4:
Tich maber onen pile, Mon'okwod wi jopinyni;
Wanayud gweth kuom tich maber Ka yie oriwo chunywa.

title: Yesu Kristo Odwaro Walame
verse1:
Yesu Kristo odwaro walem ndalowa duto te
Ochiwo Muche ni jogo Madwaro tekone.
verse2:
Yesu Kristo odwaro walame Mondo wabed matek;
Miwa winj dwondi kawuono Kwatemo luwo ka.
verse3:
Yesu Kristo odwaro walame nyaka chien'giko piny;
Eka kobiro omowa Noterwa e polo.
verse4:
Yesu Kristo odwaro walame, Ndalono chiegini;
Wamoruru kwatiyone, Kwakiyo birone.

title: Jarit Go Tung Mar Injili
verse1:
Jarit, go tun'mar Injili, Mon'inyis ji duto wach;
Ma ka n'to osewinjo, Olokre ni mon'okwo.
verse2:
Mon'igoye e wi gode, Kendo e pewe duto;
Kwonde duto, e ru ler duto, Mondo giwinj Injili.
verse3:
Kendo igoye e gwenge, Kod wan'ore duto te;
Mon'iland wach ni ji duto, Kaka Wuoro luongogi.
verse4:
Jogo be ma tin'ohewo, Magombo yudo thuolo;
Nyisgi kaka Ruoth Jawarwa, Wacho, "Biuru ira."

title: Dhiuru ,Jokristo
verse4:
Weruru, JoKristo, beduru mamor;
Wendeu medo duon'ni Kristo Jawar.
Pak, gi duon' gi teko, ni Yesu ma Ruoth,
Un gi malaika pake nyaka chien'

title: Chunya Mondo Ichiew Koro
verse1:
Chunya, mondo ichiew koro, Tim teko e tichni;
Ked Lweny maber ni Yesu Ruoth, Niyudi osimbo.
verse2:
En dwond Nyasaye moluongoi, Kowuoyo e chunyi;
Tim kinda nyaka giko, to Noruaki dalane.
verse3:
Joneno to nitie man'ny man'yoi pile;
Weche mokadho, kiki par, To teg wan' nyime.
verse4:
Teko mwakedogo e lweny, Wayudo kuomi,
Ruoth Kamano bende kwaloyo, Locho ni mari, Ruoth.

title: Jo Maler Mag Nyasaye
verse1:
Jo maler mag Nyasaye, e wachne maler
Oketonu mise madier mar genruok;
Jogo maringo ir Yesu ma Jawar,
Omiyogi singruok maber moloyo.
verse4:
"Ka Satan otemi gi temruok mager,
N'onona oromi; namiyi loyo;
Kuom temruok magerno machalo gi mach,
Adwaro pwodhi mon'ibed maler chuth."

title: Chunya, Mond' Iriti
verse1:
Chunya, mon'iritri, Wasigu lworoi;
Gitemo loyoi pile Mondo itim richo.
verse2:
Ritri galam; kedi, Ni kik ogoyi piny;
Kedi matek ndalo duto, Kikwayo kony Nyasaye.
verse3:
Locho pod ni nyime, Rit gi lwenji maber;
Tim kinda, Lweny ok enorum Nyak'yud osimbo.

title: Ok Ageno Gimoro Ngang'
verse1:
Ok ageno gimoro ngan'
To remb Yesu kod dimbruokne;
Ok dak agen n'to moro,
Ayiengora kuom nying Yesu.
verse2:
Kata mudho umo wan',
Apadora kuom n'onone;
En ok onyalo lokore,
En loch mak nyal pudhore.
verse3:
Rembe gi misango mare
E ma ageno chutho ka;
Gik man e piny kadho duto,
Ruoth Jawarna e moroma.
verse4:
En ka nobi kigoyo bu,
Mon'oyuda ka an n'te;
Koruaka gi dimbruok mare
Nabed maler e nyim kom duon'

title: Chunguru Matek Kuom Ruoth
verse1:
Chunguru matek kuom Ruoth Nyasachwa,
Kuneno chandruok, ka temruok biro;
En e tekowa, bende ngimawa
Ka richo dwaro lowa.
verse2:
Chungi kuom adier kiwuotho e piny,
Bed gi chuny maler kod yie motegno;
Kwageno Ruodhwa, wanalo chutho
Richo duto manie piny.

title: Rituru, Lemuru
Chungi Jakristo
verse2:
Kaw okumba yie, Gi ogut Konyruok,
Kendo ligangla mar  Muya,
Kik iwe lamo ma nitekoni;
Yesu okonyo askeche.
verse3:
Wuothuru matek kik uol eyo;
Yaluru pile wach Nyasaye.
Un kuti maber, Chien'kobiro
Unubed  kode e ngimane.

title: Waged E Lwanda Mangima
verse1:
Wagedi e lwanda mangima, 
kuom Yesu lwanda mochwere;
En kar Konyruokwa e piny marach,
 ka yamb temruok okudho.
verse2:
Moko gedo kuom kuoyo mayom, 
Gigeno mwandu mar pinyni;
Moko ketore kuom timbe piny,
 kuom morne to gi gombo.
verse3:
Wageduru kuom Lwanda matek
En mise ma ok nomukre;
En gi migeno ma nyaka chien' 
Genruok mar warruok marwa.

title: Awuotho Kachiko Polo
verse1:
Awuotho kachiko polo, pile amedo chorora;
Akwayo Ruoth ndalo duto, "Ruoth telna e yo mar polo".
verse2:
Chunya ok mor ka abedo kod kiawa gi luoro bende;
E pinyni ok adwar dakie, Akwayi tera e polo.
verse3:
Adwaro dak mabor gi piny, ka ma Satan ok ditema;
Kuom yie awinjo  dwol mamit, dwond wend jo maler e polo.
verse4:
Adwaro chopo e polo, Adwaro neno  ler polo;
Analem nyaka achopie, "Ruoth telna e yo mar polo."

title: Jarito Mar Dala Zayun
verse1:
Jarito mar dala Zayun, Giko piny donge chiegni?
Ineno ranyisi koso Moserieny e wan'ori?
Jawuoth, chungi, in' malo, Ler dwaro rienynwa koro;
Ruakri gi law mar kisera, Piny oyawore koro.
verse2:
Jarito, ne ler kabiro, Med menyo wan'ori;
Ranyisi ni kwonde duto, Manyiso wach birone.
Ka tun'mar polo noyuagi Jo maler ma nosetho
Ginichier e tun'piny duto, Ginyud ngima mak rum.
verse3:
Bed mamor, ler koro neno Mar ndalo maduon'mar Ruoth;
Wanahul wachni gi teko: Pinyruoth koro chiegni.
Jawuoth, tin'wan', ne loka; Duon'mar Kanaan fwenyore,
Gi dala maber mar Nyasaye, -- En Jerusalem Manyien.
verse4:
E dalano mar dhahabu, Wanane Ruoth mar Zayun
Kobedo e kom mar duon'e,koseruakore gi ler;
E pinyruodhno mar Nyasachwa Mudho ok nobedie ngan'
Gik ma wan'a pok oneno E ma wanane kuno.

title: In Migeno Chamo Mwandu Me Polo
verse1:
In migeno chamo mwandu me polo, Nan' inindo kichiegni chopo?
Chiew chunyi koro, twe gi lwenji duto; Tim kinda, to ndalo kadho piyo.
verse2:
In migeno chamo mwandu me polo, Nan' igalri kichiegni donjo?
Chungi iikri, Jawarwa obiro; Iromne kolor e boche polo.
verse3:
Timbe mag pinyni kik mon'olomb chunyi; Duto mag piny kadho kendo rumo;
Chod oko gigo mosetweyo chunyi, Kigeno chopo kawo gikeni.
verse4:
Wan' kik riwni, to mon'in' malo, Kikiyo biro mar Ruodhwa maduon'
Ndalono chiegni, lerne dwaro neno; Waikre mar romo kod Ruoth gi mor.

title: Un Jorit Mar Dala Zayun
verse1:
Un jorit mar dala Zayun, Nyiswa wach mar otieno
Ratego oneno koso? Piny dwaro runwa koso?
Ka un'yo, dong uneno ler kawuok?
Ka un'yo, dong uneno ler kawuok?
verse2:
Weche piny donge nyisowa, Wuodhwa ka ogik rumo
Wachiegni gi polo koso? Wan'a donge omake?
Wanyal geno, ka pinyruoth polo chiegni?
Wanyal geno, ka pinyruoth polo chiegni?
verse3:
Ler orienynwa, Ruodhwa biro! Onego waland wachno
Ratego koro oneno, Polo ku orieny maler
Wamoruru, warruokwa koro chiegni
Wamoruru, warruokwa koro chiegni.
verse4:
Waseyudo jatend wan'o, Wan'yo pinyno chiegni
Wadhiuru nyime piyo, Wagik donjo ka mokuwe
Waweruru, ka wajiwogo chunywa
Waweruru, ka wajiwogo chunywa.

title: Nyaka Karang'o Ruodhwa
verse1:
Nyaka karan' Ruodhwa, ma pod waritoi?
Chunywa odoko mapek Kuom rito bironi
Chien'o nobi karan' Ma piny noyawrenwa,
Mi lerni norieny kuomwa ,-- Lerni ma nyaka chien'
verse2:
Jawar, nibi karan', Ni mon'iom jogi?
To wach makuyo chunywa -- Ji nok maritoi
Jotichni josamuoyo, Ji hero weche piny;
Nitie ji manok  kende Maritoi gi mor.

title: Kristo En Jatelowa
verse1:
Kristo En jatelowa e lwenjewa, 
Ok waluoro dhiyo ka mochikowa;
Kata ok wan'yo gi man e nyimwa, 
      Wanaluwe yo duto.

title: Wakwayi, Ruoth, Kuom Tekoni
verse1:
Wakwayi, Ruoth, kuom tekoni Ma jogi chon nobedogo;
Ma nojiwo chunygi chutho,Nokonyogi dhil e chandruok.
verse2:
Ere muya ma nomiyo Ibrahim chir kuom chun'matek;
Ma notego chuny Paulo be, Kopon' gi teko maler.
verse3:
Miwa tekoni, kaka chon Elija noyudo teko;
Nonenore kuom Musa be, Nojiwo Ayub e temruok.
verse4:
Par ndalogo machon, Ruodhwa, Chiw teko kendo jiw tichni;
Kendo ka chunywa paroi Mon'iol Rohoni kuomwa.

title: Keduru Jo Ka Yesu
Yaye Mad Abed Gi Yie Chutho
verse1:
Yaye mad abed gi yie chutho,
Ma ok dak swekre ngan'
Kata wasigu lworoa,
Ka'ayudo chandruok,
Ka' ayudo chandruok.
verse2:
Yie ma ok dak obed gi n'r
Kata ayud malit;
Kata e masira malit
Ayiengra kuom Nyasaye,
Ayiengra kuom Nyasaye.
verse3:
Yieno mon'oyangre maler
Ka yamb temruok kudho;
Kata abedo ka marach
Kik abedi maluor,
Kik abedi maluor.
verse4:
Kata ka jopiny obwona,
Kata gichaya ngan'
Weche mag piny kik wuond chunya
Mar gola kuomi, Ruoth;
Mar gola kuomi Ruoth.
verse5:
Ruoth, miya yie ma kamano,
Yie ma ok lokrengan'
Kata piny bet koda marach
Agen dak kodi, Ruoth;
Agen dak kodi Ruoth.

title: Jakristo We Nindo
verse1:
Jakristo we nindo, Ruoth emochiko,
Kaw tong gi okumba kitin' e lweti;
Mon'irom gi jatem kionge luoro,
Chungi ka jachir, Kin'yo jasigu.
verse2:
Kata e chandruok, winji wach maber bed motan'
To kik idog chien, kama konyruok onge,
Oganda mag mudho, inyalo riembo,
Chungi ka jachir, kin'yo jasigu.
verse3:
Rit tich mar Ruodhi, Gi tekoni duto
Riti gi kinda, Kedi nyaka giko
Kama enotelnie, Dhi ka in jachir,
Chungi ka jachir, kin'yo jasigu.

title: Be An Jarit Msalaba
verse1:
Be an jarit msalaba, jalup mar Nyarombo?
Ok dak aluor wuot' tichne kata luongo nyinge?
verse2:
One'adhiyo e polo, gi kuwe mogundho chuth,
Ka jomamoko to kedo e dier namno mar tho?
verse3:
Aneno wasigu'uora, donge dachop kucha,
Pinyni orach onge n'ono maditera ka Ruoth.
verse4:
Adier naked mon'ayud loch Ruoth named jiwora,
Ok anadew chwat kata lit kayiengora kuomi.

title: Biuru, Jo Nyasaye
verse1:
Biuru, jo Nyasaye, Mohero En adier;
Weruruwa gi chuny achiel,
Weruruwa gi chuny achiel,
Kwachokre nyim Nyasaye,
Kwachokre nyim Nyasaye.
verse2:
Jopiny mokia Nyasaye, Biuru wadende,
To wan nyithinde wanawer,
To wan nyithinde wanawer,
Kwapako Ruodh polo,
Kwapako Ruodh polo.
verse3:
Nyithindo mag Nyasaye, Gimor ma nyaka chien'
Ka pok gitundo par Nyasaye,
Ka pok gitundo par Nyasaye,
Ka pod giwuotho ka
Ka pod giwuotho ka.
verse4:
Kata wayud chandruok E piny ma mwalo ni,
Watego wan'a kuomi, Ruoth,
Watego wan'a kuomi, Ruoth,
Kwachiko dalani
Kwachiko dalani.

title: Nitie Lweny Mager Ahinya
verse1:
Nitie lweny mager ahinya, kind adiera gi mudho,
Ka lweny obedo malich ngan' kwakedo gi jasigu,
Ruoth dwaro joma jochir,
Donge doyiengre kuomi.
verse2:
Ni gibiro gi mirima, ka gin gi teko Satan.
Giyudo teko mar jachien, Moa negi e mudho,
Ruoth dwaro joma jochir,
Donge doyiengre kuomi?
verse3:
Nyasaye wuonwa to nenowa, Malaika konyowa,
Kendo jatendwa en Yesu, ok nwarem, kata podho,
Ruoth dwaro joma jochir,
Donge doyiengre kuomi.

title: Ndalo Auchiel Oserumo
verse1:
Ndalo auchiel oserumo, Sabato ochopo kendo;
Chunya, bedi mamor chutho, Mondo irite kod n'ono.
verse2:
Wapak Ruodhwa mochiwonwa Ndalo maber mar yueyoni;
En e momiyo chunywa kuwe Moloyo ndalo duto te.
verse3:
Chunywa mondo obed mamor Kwagoyo erokamano;
Morno mondo opon'chunywa, Mosiko ma onge giko.
verse4:
Kuwe mar polo ma ni e chuny, En singruok madier mar yueyo
Moseketi e polo ku, Kar giko mar chandruok duto.

title: Sabato Mari, Ruoth
verse1:
Sabato mari, Ruoth, Jogi ruako gi mor;
Kwarito winjo wach mari Chunywa mondo paki.
verse2:
Wamor kuom ndaloni Ma isewalo, Ruoth; Wanaheri,
Wanadendi, In Ruodh polo malo.
verse3:
Jogi maler, gwedhgi! Bed kodwa kwalemo;
Ruoth, miwa mor kuom yueyoni, Kwarito chien'maler.
verse4:
Kidich piny korumo, Kwadar a thurwa ka;
Miwa dir kodi nyaka chien'E dalani maler.

title: Ruoth, Wabiro Iri
verse1:
Ruoth, wabiro iri e Skundwa mar Sabato;
Wadwaro mon'igwedhwa Kwapuonjore Wachni
In mon'ibed Japuonjwa, Iyawnwa parowa,
Ni mondo ler mar polo Omeny chunywa adier.
verse3:
Pinyni rach moloyo, Temruok nitie man'ny ngan'
To wanalo kuom Wachni Kwapidhogo e chuny
Miwa teg wan'a kuomi, In ma Jares chunywa;
Wabed jogi madieri Nyaka ndalo giko.
verse4:
Ruoth, kiw'e piny ka Mar omo jo mariti,
Wan bende mon'iyudwa Kwakiyo bironi
Eka e pinyruodh polo E Sabato pile,
To wanachokre nyimi Ni mon'imed puonjwa.

title: Mokwongo Ruodhwa Yesu
verse1:
Mokwongo Ruodhwa Yesu, noketonwa Sabato;
Kendo eka nowale, mogwedhogo ni dhano.
verse2:
Tich mar ndalowa rumo, Tinde chien'maler mar Ruoth;
Ka wadiro kuom chikne, Osingonwa gweth mare.
verse3:
Polo gi piny, nokadhi, To Sabato ok norum;
Wanadir e piny manyien, Nyaka chien'ma nyaka chien'

title: Kidira Chieng' Mar Yueyo
In Skul Marwa Mar Sabato
verse1:
In skul marwa mar Sabato In ka maler chutho;
Chunya koro gombo ywaya Mondo abi iri.
verse2:
Chunya oyudo mor chutho E skul mar Sabato 
Kasomo wach mar Ruoth Yesu Kaka nosethona.
verse3:
Yesu Ruodha man gi hera, Oluongoa mondo 
Adhi e skul mar Sabato Mon'achiwne chunya.

title: Walamo Nyasaye Tinde
E Ndaloni Maler Mar Ruoth
verse1:
E ndaloni maler mar Ruoth Chunywa oyudo mor,
Kwaweyo paro gik mag piny,Kwaparo wach Nyasaye.
verse2:
En kinde maber mar lemo, Owenwa richowa;
Watin' dwondwa kwawacho, "Wuonwa manie polo."
verse3:
Wamor kwawinjo weche kuwe moanwa ka Nyasaye,
Wamedo padore kuome, Kwachiko yor polo.
verse4:
Ka golo richo e chunywa, Otamowa nyalo,
Nyasaye on'yo dwarowa, En to okonyowa.

title: Kidich Nyasaye
verse1:
Kidich Nyasaye, ndalo mamor, Meduru paro Jakonywa;
To tinende waweyo tich Kaka Nyasaye nowachonwa.
verse2:
Nyasaye nowachonwa niya; Atieko gwedho Sabato;
To wadwaro mondo Nyasaye Omednwa gweth mare tinde.
verse3:
Keturu chunyu kuom Yesu, To en nomiu kuwe mare;
Nitie wan'o moro bende, To en modwaro witowa.

title: Nyasaye Gweth Skundwa Mar Sabato
verse1:
Nyasaye, gwedh Skundwa mar Sabato,
Bedi Jatendwa, kwachokore;
Tawa gi rieko gi herani,
Kwaluwo yori.

title: Ndalo Mamor_1
verse1:
Ndalo mamor, ma Nyasachwa
Nomiyowa e Eden chon;
Gik moko duto ma nie piny
Jachwech nomiyogi yueyo.
verse2:
Koro wadiro ndaloni
Monyisowa tich mar Nyasaye
Kwapake ka, kendo kwawer,
Chunywa opako tekone.
verse3:
Pakuru Yesu ma notho,
Kogolo Kethruok mag jopiny
Pakuru Wuod  Nyasaye man'on,
Rembe  Nochwer ni kethruokwa.
verse4:
To pok kethruok ni tho adier;
Thono Jawar noloyo,
Mondo  wawuoth e yor Nyasaye,
Mak waketho chikne maber.
verse5:
Wadwaro chikne e chunywa ka,
Wadiro tinendeni; Kendo kochweyo
Piny manyien Wanadir Sabato pile.

title: In Odira Mar Nyasaye
verse1:
In odira mar Nyasaye, In e ndalowa mar mor;
Chunye duto mor kodi, Kaka mor gi ler mar chien'
verse2:
Mor mokuwe momiyowa ohoyo chunywa adier;
Okuweyo chuny e chandruok, Nyaka wanatiek wuodhwa.
verse3:
En e ndalowa maler, mwawinje Wach Nyasachwa,
Kwapake kendo lame, mwayude n'ono mare.

title: Wachokore Gi Mor Tinde
verse1:
Wachokore gi mor tinde, kidira mar Nyasaye;
Gi mor bende wawer nyimi kwapako nyingi ka.
verse2:
Ot kama jogi lamoi Onego bed maler
Chuny ji mosayi odi ni Ilosogi maber.
verse3:
Muya Maler, Jakony man'on, Dak ie kanisa ni;
Teche liel saa duto Te Komenyo e piny.
verse4:
Nyasaye man malo, miwa mor Nyaka chunywa oyien'
A waneni Wan'gi wan' Kwamor ma nyaka chien'

title: Nyasaye, Gokiny Mond' Iwinja
verse1:
Nyasaye, gokiny mon'iwinja Ka dwonda pakoi;
In e malamoi koro Katin'ni wan'.
verse2:
Ageno Kristo ma Jawar, Masayo ni joge;
Onyiso Wuoro e polo, Yuakwa gi wendewa.
verse3:
Muche mondo taya pile E yorene maler;
Onyisa tich mone'atim, Atim gi chuny maler.
verse4:
Jo moheri kendo luori, Nichopi dwarogi;
Nyasaye maduon'oritogi, Gineno n'onone.

title: Wago Ni Ruoth Erokamano
verse1:
Wago ni Ruoth Nyasachwa erokamano ngan'
To oseritowa ma nyaka nen'okinyi.
Yesu ritwa gotienoni, kaka iseritowa chon.
verse3:
Nyasaye, bedi Jakwadhwa, kaka nisingo chon
Nikech nitie e piny ka gik moko maricho Yaye!
Yesu, winjwa koro: warwa e gik maricho gi.

title: Bedi Kod An
verse3:
Pile achando, to adwaroi,
In kendi inyalo teko mar Jachien;
In kendi itera, In midemboa,
E mudho be e chien' bedi koda.
verse4:
Onge maluoro, In kibed koda,
Eka masira dak oloya ngan'
Tho to ok rach; to liel onyal an'?
An ben'aloyogi, ka In koda.

title: Wang' Chieng Koro Podhonwa
verse1:
Wan'chien'koro podhonwa, mudho biro imo piny;
Sulwe to gi dwe koro Gotieno gidendo Ruoth.
verse2:
In mimiyowa ngima In midak e polo ku,
Lerni mon'omeny chunywa,
Ni mondo wan' adier Ka In kodwa.
verse3:
Herani obed kodwa E mudho mar otieno;
Ka nindo oterowa, Jopolo mondo ritwa Nyaka ru piny.
verse4:
Kendo chien'kiduogo, Ruoth, Gi teko mar kawo pinyruoth,
Nyasacha asayoi, Ruaka kanyo ma Intie, Polo malo.

title: Yesu ,In Ma Jahoch Mar Chuny
verse1:
Yesu, In ma Jahoch mar chuny,
Rita gotieno kanindo; Bedi koda gotienoni,
Nyaka piny chak oyawrena.
verse2:
Ka pok anindo apari Kaka ihera pile ka;
Tich Satani aseyo chuth, In Nyasaye kende madalami.
verse3:
Rita gotieno, godiechien' Ok dabed mangima mak In;
Bedi koda ka piny olil, To daluor tho da onge In.
verse4:
Kaa e nindo, Igwedha; Dhi koda ka ma adhiye;
Pile kamano nya'ibi Omo jogi moseyiei.

title: Puothe Chiek E Pinje Duto
verse1:
Puothe chiek e pinje duto, Nitie cham mathoth maber;
E pewe gi holni duto Cham orito jokeyo.
verse2:
Orgi ka chien'wuok gokinyi, Orgi kata godiechien'
Kata saa ma wan'chien'podho, pod onego gitim tich.
verse3:
Un jokeyo ma Ruoth oro, Chokuru cham mosechiek;
To ka tich me piny ka rumo Unubed gi mor maduon'

title: Winji Weche Ma Nondiki
verse1:
Winji weche ma nondiki mag Nyasaye,
"Keluru taith duto e od keno",
Waleuru chutho ni Ruodhwa maler,
Osesingo Enogwedhu.
verse2:
Udwaro n'yo teko Muya Maler?
"Keluru taith duto e od keno";
Kuwe nobed e chunyu chutho saa gi saa,
Ka uyudo gweth mowacho.
verse3:
Gimoro ogen'koso gweth mar Ruoth,
Keluru taith duto e od keno;
Ji mamako wach mar Yesu Kristo Ruoth,
Yudo hawi pile Kuome.

title: Richona Diluok Gang'o
verse1:
Richona diluok gan'? Mana gi remb Yesu kende.
En an' ma dipwodha? Mana gi remb Yesu kende.
verse2:
Onge gi ma dipwodha, to mana remb Yesu kende;
Aonge chandruok moro, mana gi remb Yesu kende.
verse3:
Ok anyal yudo winjruok, mak mana gi remb Ruoth Yesu;
Bura to bwogo chunya, kaonge gi remb Ruoth Yesu.
verse4:
Ma e genona kende, en e remo mar Ruoth Yesu;
Aonge ber kata kuwe, mak mana kuom remb Ruoth Yesu.
verse5:
Gi moromo ji duto, en remo mar Ruodhwa Yesu;
Achiwo pakna duto, ni remono mar Ruoth Yesu.

title: Ringra Namiyo In
Adwaro Manyo Rombe Mabayo
verse1:
Adwaro manyo rombe mobayo, Mondo gibi ir Yesu Jakwath;
Anyisgi weche kaka owacho, "Biuru ira, aherou."
verse2:
Adwaro manyo rombe mobayo, Mondo anyisgi Yesu Jawar;
Mondo akelgi, duto giyudi Ngima mochwere mosingonwa.
verse3:
Mano e tich ma adwaro timo, tinde awinjo koluongae;
Mondo atin'rombe mosepodho, akelgi ir Jakwadha Maber.

title: Yesu Oluongoi Mondo Ibi
verse1:
Yesu oluongoi mondo ibi, Oluongoi kawuononi;
Nikech oneno kibayo marach, Kidhiyo mabor kode.
verse2:
Yesu oluongo jo mool giyuwe, Oluongou kawuononi;
Kelne tin'duto machandi pile, En ok noriembi kodgi.
verse3:
Yesu oriti, bi ire tinde, Oritoi kawuononi;
Bi ire, nyise richoni duto; Reti, to kik ideki.
verse4:
Yesu osayo, dak iwinj dwonde; Yie winj dwonde, kawuononi;
Jogo moyie nyinge giniyud mor, Chungi, dhi ire piyo.

title: Nitie Wendo E Dhoot
verse2:
Koro yawne, Ruodh chunyi; Dak yawne, to kideko nokadhi,
Dak yawne; Ruake nikech En Osiep, kendo enorit chunyi,
Enoriti nyaka chien' Dak yawne.
verse3:
Winji dwonde kosayo; Dak yawne; En ma mondo iyiere,
Dak yawne; Ochungo e dhoot oko, Orito mon'iyawne,
Enomedni mor gi kuwe; Dak yawne.
verse4:
Ruakuru wendo polo, dak yawne; Enotimni mor maduon'
Dak yawne; Enowenu richou, kendo twech maru nogony,
Enoteru ka maler, dak yawne.

title: Yesu Oluongowa Koro
verse1:
Yesu oluongowa koro gi n'ono,
Oluongo in kod an be;
Ochungo oko e dhoranga chunywa,
Korito in kod an be.
verse2:
Yesu osayo, maran' wakedo?
Osayo in kod an be;
Wadeko nan' kwachako n'onone?
On'onone kod an be.
verse3:
Ndalo okadho, okadho mapiyo,
Kadho ni in kod an be;
Pinyo biro rumo, tho chikowa koro,
Ochiko in kod an be.
verse4:
Paruru hera maduon'ma osingo,
mosingoni kod an be;
Kata waketho, oyie wenwa kethwa,
Oyie weni kod an be.

title: Nawinjo Yesu Kowacho
verse3:
Nawinjo Yesu kowacho, "Abedo ler mar piny;
N'ya koro, mudho orum, nibed gi ler pile."
Nan'yo Yesu, mayudo, ler kaka mar wan'chien'
Nawuothi koro e lerno nyaka wuodha norum.

title: Yesu Jakwath Madieri
verse1:
Yesu Jawkath madieri, Oluongou tinde; 
Mondo udonj e kunde, To nunwan'kuwe maber. 
Biuru jo madongo, Biuru nyithindo, 
Donju'e kul mar Yesu, To En Jakwath maber.
verse3:
Kwadeko to wafuwo, Satan ni e piny ka, 
Kotemo mako rombe, odwaro negogi. 
Yesu Jakwath madieri, oluongou koro; 
Donju'e kul mar Yesu, To en Jakwath maber.

title: Winji Dwond Yesu Kawuono
verse1:
Winji duond Yesu kawuono, "N' madhiyo tich tinde? 
Ji mathoth ma pok on'yo, N' madhiyo nyisogi?" 
Yesu chikowa ahinya, Enopogwa pok maber; 
N' madwokne piyo piyo, "Era e; ora, ora."
verse3:
Mitki ok dibed jayalo, Mobedo kaka jarit 
Mar nyiso ji wan'yor ngima, Yorno mochiko polo. 
To gi lemo, bende michni, Inyalo konyo tich Ruoth;  
Kamano nichal kod Harun, Kitego jotich Nyasaye.
verse4:
Ka Yesu oluongi pile, Ka ji thoth madwaro tho, 
Kik iwach awacha kende, "Onge moro ma datim," 
Yie tichno ma Yesu miyi, Tich mamiyo chunyi mor; 
En koluongi, dwoke piyo, " Era e, ora, ora."

title: Wasewinjo Wach Maber
verse2:
Weruru pile pile, Yesu ni Jawarwa;
Ne otho kendo nochier, Yesu ni Jawarwa.
Weruru ni ji matuo, ka giwinjo rem malit,
Weruru e kar liete, Yesu ni Jawarwa.
verse3:
Ne wakia wechegi, Yesu ni Jawarwa; 
Koro wan wamor nikech Yesu ni Jawarwa, 
Ne wadak e mudho chuth, ti waneno ler Nyasaye, 
E momiyo mudho tur, Yesu ni Jawarwa.
verse4:
Yaluru e piny ma ka, Yesu ni Jawarwa 
Yaluru e pinje te, Yesu ni Jawarwa; 
Kik wadeki, kik walin' nyaka Yesu oduogi, 
Nyaka ji duto on', Yesu ni Jawarwa.

title: Ng'a Mowinjo Dwond Ruoth
verse2:
"N' mobiro ira," Yesu wacho, 
"Kik odeki to mondo obi piyo. 
An e Yo, Adiera, kendo an Ngima; 
N' mowinjo dwonda, bi."

title: Dhoranga Polo Yawore
verse1:
Dhoranga polo yawore, Wayud kinde mar neno 
Ler moa e msalap Yesu, Manyisowa herane.
verse2:
Rangano pod oyawore Ni joma richo duto, 
Madongo gi matindo be, Magombo yudo warruok.
verse3:
Watimuru kinda koro, Wayie n'ono maduon'o; 
Kwatin' msalaba koro, Wanayudi osimbo.
verse4:
Ka wasekalo aora, To wanawe msalaba; 
Ruoth nomiwa ngima mak rum, Wanahere mochwere.

title: Jathieth Maduong' Osudo Ka
verse1:
Jathieth maduon'osudo ka, En Yesu ma Jakonywa;  
Wachne omiyo chunya mor, Yaye, winjuru dwonde.
verse2:
Oseweyoni richoni, Winji Yesu kowacho; 
Chunyi koro obed gi kuwe, Kichiko wan'yor polo.
verse3:
Wadend Nyarombono motho; Koro ayie kuom Yesu. 
Ahero nyin'mar Jawarna, Ahero nyin'o, Yesu.
verse4:
Nyin'o ogolo richona, Onge maromo kode;
Chunya mor nade kawinjo Nyin'o maber mar Yesu.
verse5:
Koduogo chiwo osimbo, Osimb ngima mar locho
Eka wanabedi bute, Wanadend Jawar Yesu.

title: Richo Oketho Ji Malit
verse1:
Richo oketho ji malit, Okelo buch Nyasaye;
Doteri ka marach chutho, to Yesu gudoi.
verse2:
Yesu otho nitho adier, misango mar Nyasaye;
Oluoko kethni duto te, gi rembe ma nochwer.
verse3:
Ee, Yesu En e yo adier, materoi maber;
En bende to owuothoe, odwaro kowo in.
verse4:
Bi chak iwuothie koro ka, ka pod ingima in;
Yesu owuon oluongoi, oluongoi adier.

title: Yesu Okadho
verse1:
Yesu okadho, Yesu okadho, Un jo mamuofni biuru ire; 
Yesu noruaku, kendo nochangu,
Wengeu noyepi mondo unen; Biuru! 
Yesu nomiu neno.

title: Ngima Machiek Mawango
verse1:
Ngima machiek mawango, chalo gi pot yath malwar, 
Chalo 'boke matop, ret piyo;
Ndalo nyiso wa adier ni n'ono chiegni rumo, 
N'ono nyalo rumoni ret piyo.
verse2:
Thiepe mag piny biro lal, joma tindo biro ti, 
Ok in gi kinde malach, Ret piyo, 
Ka Nyasaye luongoi, In jaricho we bayo 
Dipo kisi'e richo, Ret piyo.
verse3:
Ndalo to kadho piyo, tho kod bura chiegini, 
Ringi idhi ir Yesu, Ret piyo, 
Akwayi ibed mariek dipo ndalo on'di, 
Kendo ilal mochwere Ret piyo.
verse4:
In jaricho winj duonde, yier Yesu mondo otelni, 
Eka jopolo nomor, Ret piyo, 
Ringi iae mudho, Bi ipuodhri ir Yesu,
Yie ichak wuoth tinende, Ret piyo.

title: Yie Yesu Odonj E Chunyi
verse1:
Ka iol gi tin' chandruok richo; Ruak Yesu Jawar e chunyi;
Ka idwaro chako ngima manyien, Yie Yesu odonj e chunyi.
verse2:
Ka ikuyo nikech richo magi, Ruak Yesu Jawar e chunyi; 
Soko mar Puodhruok iyudo kuome, yie Yesu odonj e chunyi.
verse3:
Ka nitie temruok motamo chunyi, Ruak Yesu Jawar e chunyi;
Ka en tem ma pinyni ok onyal golo, Yie Yesu odonj e chunyi.
verse4:
Ka osiepni machon oweyi, Ruak Yesu Jawar e chunyi; 
Pim osiep Yesu gi mago machon, Yie Yesu e chunyi.
verse5:
Ka diher wero wend jomolocho, Ruak Yesu e chunyi; 
Ka diher donje dala mar yueyo, Yie Yesu donj e chunyi.

title: Be Iseyudo Jawar Maber
verse1:
Be Iseyudo Jawar maber, moloyo duto me piny, 
Mochiwo ngima mar wari, motho chuth ni richoni.
verse2:
Be iseyudo Jawar maber mokadho e liel ne in, 
Mochodo tuech mar thoni, tekone nyalo resi.
verse3:
Be iseyudo Jawar maber, be in'yo muolo gi kuwe,
Mopon' chuny ji magene, ma heragi tut kuome.
verse4:
Be iseyudo Jawar maber, dware ma onge deko, 
Bil mitne maonge deko, nogol richowa oko.

title: Bi Ka Yesu
verse1:
Bi ka Yesu, bi ka Yesu, Bi ka Yesu koro; 
Koro ini bika Yesu, Bi ka Yesu koro.
verse2:
En Jakonyi, En Jakonyi, En Jakonyi koro; 
Koro En onyalo konyi, Bi ka Yesu koro.
verse3:
En gi teko, En gi teko, En gi teko koro; 
Yesu En onyalo duto, Bi ka Yesu koro.
verse4:
In kidware, In kidware, In kidware koro; 
Yesu koro bendo dwari, Bi ka Yesu koro.
verse5:
Sae koro, Sae koro, Sae Yesu koro; 
Yesu ruako joma saye, Bi ka Yesu koro.

title: Winji Jawar Ni E Dhoot
verse1:
Winji Jawar ni e dhoot irwake, irwake, irwake;
Oseduon' gi kinda irwake, irwake, irwake.
verse2:
En osiepni madieri, irwake, irwake, irwake;
En onyalo siroi irwake, irwake, irwake.
verse3:
Kik oduon'kayiem nono, irwake, irwake, irwake;
Dipo ka ok oduogo irwake, irwake, irwake.
verse4:
Winji duonde mar hera, irwake, irwake, irwake;
Ruake e chuny gi mor irwake, irwake, irwake.

title: Un Jo Mojony, Biuru
verse2:
"Biuru, un muruenyo, to anamiu ler;"
Dwond Yesu'oyo chunywa ka mudho imowa
Chunywa nepon'gi kuyo, Wan'o noselalnwa;
To osemiyowa mor, Wadende koro.
verse4:
"N' manade mabiro ok anajwan' ngan'"
Ok wanyal go kiawa kwawinjo dwond Yesu;
Oluongowa - moketho, wan jo mak winjre ngan'
Gi herane gi n'ono; Wabironi, Ruodhwa.

title: Chungo E Adiera Kaka Daniel
verse1:
Chungo e adiera e winjo chik Nyasaye;
Waluor jo manok moyie jogo gin lang Daniel.
verse2:
Ji ma rateke gilal nikech ok gi chun'
Ma dobedo jo Nyasaye da gin gi lang Daniel.
verse3:
Ji mathoth ma rabede ma wuotho e piny;
Gore piny matek malich komonj gi lang Daniel.
verse4:
Tin'wach mar ritruok malo nyaka ilochi;
Tam Satan gogandane riwri gi lang Daniel.

title: Nitie Remo Ma Nochwer
verse3:
Remb Nyarombo ma nonegi, Obedo gi teko 
Mar pwodho jogo magene, Ni kik giketh kendo. 
Ni kik giketh kendo, Ni kik giketh kendo; 
Mar pwodho jogo magene, Ni kik giketh kendo.
verse4:
Nyaka nageno remono Mochwer e Kalwari, 
Apako hera mar Jawar, Moherowa kama. 
Moherowa kama, Moherowa kama; 
Apako hera mar Jawar, Moherowa kama.
verse5:
Ruoth, ka'an n' marach kama,Kuom n'ononi maduon'
Isewara, ilosona, Kar bet ma nyaka chien'
Kar bet ma nyaka chien' Kar bet ma nyaka chien'
Isewara, ilosona, Kar bet ma nyaka chien'

title: Ruoth Yesu, Agombo Bedo Nga'ti
Abiro Ni Msalaba
verse1:
Abiro ni msalaba, an ayom, an n' modhier;
Aweyo gi piny duto, Mon'akwo e msalaba.
verse2:
Ayuakni koro, Jawar, Richo e moloyoa;
Yesu to wacho niya, "Anawe gi duto te."
verse3:
Achiwoni duto te, ngimana kod tekona;
Chunya kod ringra bende, Nobed mari nyaka chien'
verse4:
Kuom rembi manochwerna, aseluokora koro;
Aweyo gombo duto, analuwi, Jawarna.
verse5:
Yesu bi, ipon'chunya, mon'abed molony kuomi;
Abedi maler chutho, mon'apaki nyaka chien'

title: Agombo Bedo Gi Ruodha
verse1:
Agombo bedo gi Ruodha, nikech agombo bet maler; 
En koluoka gi pi gi mach, nabed maler, nabed mapoth.
verse2:
Kinyisa, kendo ipuonja, nabed mamor, nabed moil; 
Ka chunya ler, ka chunya poth, nabed mamor, mamor chutho.
verse3:
Ka pod arem bedo maler, ok anyal n'yo puonj maber;
Puonja, Muya Maler, Jahoch; Iluok chunya, abed mapoth.
verse4:
Awuon e chunya, ee Ruodha, aseko kwerora matek, 
Ni mon'abed maler e Ruoth; To pok ayudo teko, Ruoth.

title: Analu Bang' Yesu
verse1:
Analu ban'Yesu Nyarombo Nyasaye, 
Noluoka gi rembe mosechwer; 
Hera mare e momiyo'honwa ka, 
Noluoka gi rembe mosechwer.
verse2:
Analu ban'Yesu Kristo Jakonywa, 
Noluoka gi rembe mosechwer; 
Rembe e moromo mana ji duto, 
Noluoka gi rembe mosechwer.
verse3:
Analu ban'Yesu Kristo jagwethna, 
Noluoka gi rembe mosechwer; 
Enoyie ni mon'adonji e polo, 
Noluoka gi rembe mosechwer.
verse4:
Kethna duto ni mon'ahul ni Nyasaye, 
Noluoka gi remb Yesu Wuode; 
Mondo miya ngimane ma nyaka chien' 
Noluoka gi rembe mosechwer.

title: Asebayo Mabor Kod Ruoth
verse1:
Asebayo mabor kod Ruoth, koro aduogo; 
Asebayo marach chutho, koro aduogo.
verse2:
Asebayo ndalo man'ny, Koro aduogo; 
Chunya olokreni, Ruodha, koro aduogo.
verse3:
Awito keth kod tim marach, koro aduogo; 
Nagen herani kod wachni, koro aduogo.
verse4:
Yesu Ruodha, isewara, An abironi; 
Nitho e Kalwari ni an, An abironi.
verse5:
Pwodha gi rembi mochwerna, an abironi; 
Luoka, abed maler chutho, Ruoth, abironi.

title: Jawar Owachona
verse1:
Jawar owachona, "Tekoni tin adier; 
One'iritri galam, iniyud duto kuoma."
verse2:
Ruoth, koro aneno, teko mari kende; 
Manyalo pwodha maler, kendo golna chuny matek.
verse3:
Aonge gi maber, ageno n'ononi; 
Luoka, guda, pwodha chuth, gi remb Nyaromb Kalwari.
verse4:
Ka nachun'e nyim duon' nabed molony kuome; 
Gi loch duto maayudo, naket e tiend Ruoth Yesu.

title: Yesu,Kar Msalabani
verse1:
Yesu, kar msalabani, Nitie soko maler, 
Aora machango tuo, Machwer a Kalwari.
verse2:
Kanyo e kar msalaba, Herani noyuda; 
An naluor, to In in'on, Nimenya gi lerni.
verse3:
Miya paro thoni, Ruoth, Kod rembi mochwerna; 
Konya bed buti pile, Ni mon'ichik wuodha.
verse4:
Ruodha, mond asiki Kanyo but msalaba, 
Kakiyo be kageno, Biro mari, Ruodha.

title: Duto Amiyo Ruoth Yesu
verse1:
Duto amiyo Ruoth Yesu, amiye chunya duto; 
Anahere ndalo duto, analuwe pile ka.
verse2:
Duto amiyo Ruoth Yesu, anagone chonga piny; 
An aweyo mor mag pinyni, kawa Yesu, kawa chuth.
verse3:
Duto amiyo Ruoth Yesu, Losa, abed nyathini; 
Miya Roho mari, Ruodha, Orita ndalo duto.
verse4:
Duto amiyo Ruoth Yesu; An ayudo mor maduon' 
Kaparo kaka nowara, nadend nyinge nyaka chien'

title: Yesu Luongi, We Ting'ni Mar Richo
verse3:
Yie mon'ibed matar moloyo pe, 
Nitie teko e remb Nyarombo;
Noruch keth duto ibedi maler, 
Kuom teko mar remb Nyarombo.
verse4:
Yie mondo itim tich Ruodhwa Yesu, 
Nitie teko e remb Nyarombo;
Yie mon'idend nyinge ndalo duto, 
Kuom teko mar remb Nyarombo.

title: Nitie Ng'ama Noyie Tho Mondo Owara
verse1:
Nitie n'ma noyie tho mondo owara, 
Mondo an marach ayud ngima. 
Kendo yor kalwari noluwo kodhi tho, 
Mondo owe richona duto.
verse2:
En man'on kendo ber, okecha pile ka 
Oluoko chunya be mochido.
Aonge bura moro, an thuolo chutho 
Nikech kethna duto nosegur.
verse3:
Anasik kuom Jawarna, ok anaweye, 
Anawuoth gi mor ndalo duto,
Ka awer gi dhoga kod wend pak e chunya, 
Nikech kethna duto nosegol.

title: In Kiol Nikech Chandruok
verse1:
In Kiol nikech chandruol e chunyi,
Dhi inyis Yesu parruokni duto;
Onge osiep moro kaka Yesu,
Dhi inyis Yesu kende.
verse2:
Kata mirima ohingo chunyi,
Dhi inyis Yesu parruokni duto;
Tin'mapek kodwaro loyo chunyi,
Dhi inyis Yesu Kende.
verse3:
In kiluoro chandruok gi masiche,
Dhi inyis Yesu parruokni duto;
Kik ichandori ni gi mabiro,
Dhi inyis Yesu kende.
verse4:
Ka luoro mar tho obwogo chunyi, 
Dhi inyis Yesu parruokni duto; 
Kidwaro bedo e pinyruodh polo, 
Dhi inyis Yesu kende.

title: Nitie Ngima Kwang'iyo Msalaba
verse1:
Nitie ngima kwan'yo msalaba; 
Yesu wacho, "N'yauru." 
Mwandu mar piny en gi mokadho,  
Mwandu mosiko ni kuom Ruoth Yesu.
verse2:
Ka nakwongo n'yo wan'Jawarna, 
Non'yoa gi wan'man'on; 
Kendo ka temruok dwaro loya,  
Nayud teko kan'yo msalaba.
verse3:
Nan' msalaba ndalona duto, 
Kageno singruok mar Nyasaye; 
Satani ok onyalo loyo  
Jogo mageno teko mar polo.

title: Ka Satan Otemi
verse1:
Ka Satan otemi, kodwaro loyi,
Ka chunyi oani e masicheni;
Par Yesu Jawarni ndalo mokonyi,
En nosiri koro, pod oheroi.
verse2:
Koso in Jakristo man gi chuny mapek,
Tin' msalabani bedo matek?
Par Yesu Jawarni, Chuny mapek noa,
Iniyud mor koro, kaa e piny ka.
verse3:
Kineno jo moko man gi pith mag piny,
Mwandugi nokadhi ndalo giko piny;
Par Yesu Jawarni, Ruoth polo malo.
Gen moloyo Kristo gi pok masiko.
verse4:
Kendo e lwenje mon'ibed n't mager,
Wach mar miriambo lo gi wach maber;
Yesu ma Jawarni gi malaika,
Ginimor moloyo e polo kucha.

title: Anayie Ruoth Yesu Kende
verse1:
Anayie Ruoth Yesu kende, asewinjo wach mare; 
Onge gi manyalo loyo n'to mogeno Yesu.
verse2:
Kethna duto awe kuome, enoluoka gi rembe; 
Enorita nyaka chien'ka notera ka Nyasaye.
verse3:
Koro ok aluor gi moro, chunya koro genoi; 
Kata yora timo mudho, Yesu ni lerna pile.
verse4:
Chunya amiyo Ruoth Yesu, ringra bende amiye; 
Ndalo duto enorita nyaka chien'a noduogi.

title: Geno Kristo Kelonwa Mor
Nyasaye Noolnwa Gweth Polo
verse1:
Nyasaye noolnwa gweth polo, Kaka koth chwe e piny;
E ma nosingo kod joge, E ma nokelnwa kony.
verse2:
Nyasaye noolnwa gweth polo, Mon'ochiew chunywa koro;
Kaka koth biro maduon'gan' Aore duto kopon'
verse3:
Nyasaye noolnwa gweth polo, Enonyiswa n'onone;
Olnwa ni mondo wachungi, Mondo wadongni, Ruodhwa.
verse4:
Nyasaye noolnwa gweth polo, Mondo ogudhnwa koro;
Wanahul kethowa duto, Yienwa, Yesu, kwaluongi.

title: Ka Chandruok Osudo Machiegni Kodi
verse1:
Ka chandruok osudo machiegni kodi, 
Ka yo man e nyimi otimo mudho, 
Nitie ler mogwedhi man kuom Ruoth Yesu, 
Monego in' mondo ilo temruok.
verse2:
Kata ok in'yo tiend tin'i mapek, 
Mosechandi e ngimani e piny ka; 
Mon'itin'msalapi e chandruok duto, 
Kendo igen Yesu ndalo duto te.
verse3:
Dhi nyime kuom yie mondo ilo temruok, 
Kin'yo ka Jawar ni buti pile; 
Kata ka lweny tek to kik chunyi oa, 
Jawar nokonyi mondo ilo temruok.
verse4:
Kata lweny ger chutho,  kata kuyo thoth, 
Kata temruok duon'machiegni hingoi; 
Ruoth ni buti pile nomiyi teko, 
Mar loyo temruok duto mabironi.

title: Beduru Gi Yie
verse1:
Beduru gi yie kaka Yohana, kaka notiyo ni Nyasaye; 
Notere e chula mar Patimo, Ne oyudo chwat malit.
verse2:
Beduru gi yie kaka Yakobo, kaka nobedo gi Nyasaye; 
Moneno ngas moa polo, Jomalaika ne gintie.
verse3:
Beduru giyie kaka Yosef, kaka nobedo gi Nyasaye; 
Noloyo tem ma nothun', E od Ruoth Farao.
verse4:
Beduru giiyie kaka Elija, kaka nobedo gi Nyasaye; 
Notere e polo kongima, e gari moliel mach.
verse5:
Beduru gi yie kaka Daniel, ma nene obole e bur sibuoche;
Gokinyi noyude kongima, Dario ne owuoro ngan'

title: Chunyi Dich Nikech Parruok
verse1:
Chunyi dich nikech parruok, Dak imi Yesu kinde? 
Weche piny otweyoi, Dak imi Yesu kinde?
Ne ochungo e dhoot Odwon' mon'iyawne; 
Winje koro kosayo- Dak imi Yesu kinde.
verse2:
Saa okadhoni nono, Dak iti tich mar Yesu? 
Nyasaye nomiyi teko, Mond iti tich mar Yesu,
Dak item loyo richo, Dak ikony jo moketho, 
Dwaro jogo mobayo yo, Dak iti tich mar Yesu?
verse3:
In midwaro gik mag piny, Dak ipar Yesu Ruodhwa? 
Yaw chunyi ni tim maber, Kitiyo ni Ruoth Yesu, 
Mor mag piny gi mwandune, Kelo mor e chuny dhano; 
To ok en mor mosiko; Dak wami Yesu kinde?
verse4:
Ka dwabed pot yath kende; To ok wanyag olembe. 
Luetewa nobed nono, Ndalo maduon'mar keyo; 
Onge gi mwakel chien'o, Tichwa nobedi kayiem, 
Mi ok wanayud mor ngan' Kwaromo gi Ruoth Yesu.

title: Un Muhero Ruoth Polo
verse1:
Un muhero Ruodh polo, Weruru kuwuotho ka;
Wendewa omedo duon'Ni Yesu ma Jawarwa.
verse2:
Wan wadwaro piny maber, Kaka kwerewa machon;
Yesu e motelonwa, Obedo Jakwath man'on.
verse3:
Kik waluor masiche wuoth, thurwa koro chiegini;
Wanane Jatelowa, Ok nowewa nyaka chien'
verse4:
Wuothuru, Jowetewa; Kik wariwre e wan'o;
Yueyo to oritowa, Wanacham mwandu kuno.

title: Nyasaye Ni Lerna
verse2:
Nyasaye ni lerna, e chandruok duto,
Kata ok anene, chunya ogene;
Mudho mar Satani ok anoloya
Ka Yesu obedo koda.

title: Koro Wagenoi
verse3:
Ka wadak e piny ka, ka chunywa okuyo, Yesu konywa
Ruodhwa, dag e chunywa, Bedi Jahochwa ka
Chien'moro iterwa Polo malo.

title: Ang'eyo Wuonwa Ong'eyo
verse2:
An'yo Wuonwa on'yo, yath madikuwena rem mara;
Komula gi luete maler, nochangi chunyani matuwo, nochangi chunyani matuwo.

title: Kat' Abed Jaketh Maduong'
verse2:
Hera Yesu duon'chutho, Onyiso polo malo,
Tut moloyo nam matut, Osiko ma nyaka chien'
Herane noywayoa, Nogola e mudho ka.

title: Adwari Saa Duto
verse1:
Adwari saa duto, Yesu man'on;
Adwaro tekoni, to an ayom.
verse2:
Adwari saa duto, sudi buta;
Satan ok oloya, ka an abuti.
verse3:
Adwari saa duto, e mor gi tuo;
To an kaonge in, anyal an'?
verse4:
Adwari saa duto, puonja wachni;
Tim ka'idwaro In, an nyathini.
verse5:
Adwari saa duto, Yesu Ruodha;
An n'ti chutho, an, ndalo duto.

title: Kata Ka Abedo Gi Ngima Maber
verse4:
Ruoth Yesu, ru ndalono mar bironi,
Ma wanawinj dwond tun'machien kaneni kibiro e boche polo
Anabedi gi kuwe e chunya.

title: Kwawuotho Gi Ruodhwa
verse2:
Ka wachandore ka, ka waneno malit,
Wach Nyasaye nyalo boyo chunywa;
Ok wanyal chwanyore, ok wanyal chandore,
To Ruoth Yesu on'yo duto.
verse3:
Koro ok wanaluor ka wabedo kode,
Ka Ruoth Yesu owuotho kodwa;
Wanan' herane ka wachiworene,
Eka wanamor kuome pile.
verse4:
Ka wahere kama, ka wawinjo chikne,
Wanadhi ku moorowae;
Kik wapar rem moro, Yesu oritowa,
Wan to mondo wagene kende.
verse5:
Chien'ka Yesu biro, eka wananene,
Bende wanamor gi Jawarwa;
Kuyo ok wanane, kata chandruok moro,
Wanadag kode e dalane.

title: An Ayie Ruoth Yesu Kende
verse1:
An ayie Ruoth Yesu kende, Asewinjo wach mare;
Onge gi manyalo loyo N'to mogeno Yesu.
verse2:
Kethna duto awe kuome, En oluoka gi rembe;
Enorita nyaka ndalo Ka notera ka Nyasaye.
verse3:
Koro ok aluor gimoro, Chunya ogeno Yesu;
Kata yora timo mudho, Yesu ni lerna pile.
verse4:
Chunya asemiyo Yesu, Ringra bende amiye;
Yesu, Jahera, Osiepna, Nobed koda nyaka chien'

title: Yesu Kristo En Osiepwa
verse2:
Ka Satani dwaro temwa, ka masira makowa,
Chunywa kik oa kuom Yesu, ber kwanyiso Yesu wach;
Ere n'to ma dikonywa kuom masira manie piny?
Yesu emon'yo nyawowa, ber kwanyiso Yesu wach.

title: Ruoth, Ok Akwayoi Tinde
Ruoth En E Jakwadha
Tim Kinda Mar Lemo
Winj Weche Ma Yesu Nowacho
verse3:
Jogo ma nodonji e dala, jo maler, maonge richo,
Jo mowar, mopwodhi, e remb Nyarombo,
Ginichopi e yath mar ngima.

title: Wuothi E Ler Mar Ruoth Nyasaye
verse1:
Wuothi e ler mar Ruoth Nyasaye, mamenyo wan'ori;
Muche maler, moa malo, nyalo riembo mudho.
verse2:
Wuothi e ler mar puonj Ruodhwa, moa kuom Wach Nyasaye;
Ler matelo ni nyithindo, moyie Weche Nyasaye.
verse3:
Wuothi kata mudho olil modino wan'ori;
Mudho noringi e nyim ler, mar Ruoth ma nyaka chien'
verse4:
Wuothi e ler eka nin' kaka Ruoth oheri;
Wanabed gi winjruok maduon' moloyo mar piny ka.

title: Ka Yesu Ni Koda
verse3:
Ka Yesu ni koda ok an kenda ngan'
Ka'osiepe weya to En Osiepna;
To kata otera e yore malich,
Ka Yesu ni koda to nabed mamor.

title: Yesu En Osiep Maber Chutho
verse3:
Kata kuyo malit oyuda, kata kachopo e saa thona,
kibaji ok nogoya, nikech Jawar En koda,
Ee, Yesu En Osiep maber ngan'
verse4:
Ka wachokre e thurwa malo, Kachiel gi jogo ma notho chon,
Wanawer mamit kucha, kwadende ma nyaka chien'
Yesu En Osiep maber moloyo.

title: Owadwa Kik Iluor
verse1:
Owadwa kik iluor, Bedi gi chir pile;
Nyasaye none masicheni, On'yo hoyoi.
verse2:
Kata ka chunyi lit, Ka gigi kethore;
Kik chunyi ol, kik chunyi a, Nyasaye nomii kuwe.
verse3:
Otieno to norum, Chien'mar dimbruok nobi;
Masicheni duto nolal Ka Ruoth ofwenyore.
verse4:
Gen hera mar Ruodhi, Onge motamo En;
Bedi pile e luetene, Noriti nyaka chien'

title: Yesu Ni Jakwadha
Ruoth Yesu, Saa Mar Lamoi
Saa Mar Lemo Mogwedhi
Analu Bang'i Jakonya
verse1:
Analu ban', Jakonya, Ka midwaro telona;
Ku midhiye analuwi, Adwaro luwo ban'.
verse2:
Kata yo otimo thuche, Kata kudho chwowoa,
Isedhiyo yorno nyima, Adwaro luwo ban'.
verse3:
Kata abedo gi chandruok, Kata Satan temoa;
Kahingo notemi bende, Adwaro luwo ban'.
verse4:
Kata ayudo masira, Kabedo n' ma jachan,
In'yo chandruok me piny ka; Adwaro luwo ban'.
verse5:
Ka di po malit oyuda, Kendo ngimana rumo;
Mano gi min'yo duto, Adwaro luwo ban'.

title: Weruru Weche Mag Nyasaye
verse2:
Yesu miyo ji duto te, weche mamit mag ngima.
Ji moketho winjuruwa, weche mamit maber,
Yesu miyogi nono, ji mondo yiegi kende.

title: To Kak Abet Yesu Kawa
verse1:
To kak abet yesu kawa, Inyisa yo maber chutho;
Abironi, iwachona, Ruodhwa Yesu, abironi.
verse2:
To ka'abet Yesu yiea, Adwaro mond iluok chunya;
To in iwe kethruok maga Ruodhwa Yesu, abironi.
verse3:
To ka'abet Yesu kawa, Imiyo chunya mor pile;
Ndalo duto chunya bayo, Ruodhwa Yesu, abironi.
verse4:
To ka'abet ni an muofu, an n' modhier morem teko;
In kende In Jakinda ngan' Ruodhwa Yesu, abironi.
verse5:
To ka'abet Yesu kawa, Iruaka, luoka, guda ka;
Nikech ageno singruokni, Ruodhwa Yesu, abironi.

title: Awinjo Dwondi Maler
verse1:
Awinjo dwondi maber Moluonga iri, Ruoth;
Mon'iluok chunya gi rembi, Ma nochwer Kalwari.
verse2:
An arach moloyo ji, Aonge gi teko;
Adwaro mon'iluoka chuth, Mon'abedi mapoth.
verse3:
Yesu, In kibet koda, Koro natim maber;
Satani ok anonyal loya, Kabedo nyathini.
verse4:
Ka pod an ie piny ka, Adwaro puonjo ji;
Kuom remb Yesu manochwernigi, E yath mar Kalwari.
verse5:
Yesu In kiwi'e piny, Mondo iom jogi;
Wanadhi kodi e polo, E dalani maler.

title: An Ni Mari Ruoth
verse1:
An ni mari, Ruoth, to niluongoa; Isenyisa herani;
To adwaro in mon'ibed koda, Mon'ibed koda pile.
verse2:
Adwaro mondo ati tichni, Ruoth; Adwaro mon'ikonya;
Mondo apari ndalo duto te, kik agomb mokome piny.
verse3:
An amor pile ka atiyoni, Ka chunya oheroi;
Ka Alamo in, ka iwinjoa, Ka abedo nyathini.
verse4:
Herani matut ok anyal n'yo, Nyaka atundi kuno;
Mor man e polo okadho n'yo; Nyaka ayud kuwe kuomi.

title: Kaw Piny Duto Miya Yesu
verse1:
Kaw piny duto; miya Yesu; Mor mar piny  to mana nono;
Hera Yesu ok olokre, To osiko nyaka chien'
verse2:
Kaw piny duto; miya Yesu; En jahoch chutho mar chuny;
Ka Jawarna e marita, Nawer kata kuom chandruok.
verse3:
Kaw piny duto miya Yesu, Mon'an' wan' mamor;
Ndalo duto kuom wuodha ka Enomenyna wan'ora.
verse4:
Kaw piny duto; miya Yesu; Ageno msalabane;
Eka chien'ka Ruodhwa biro, Ananene wan'gi wan'

title: Kaw Ngimana
verse1:
Kaw ngimana, mon'abed mari chutho, Yesu Ruoth.
Kaw ndalona duto te; gibedi ka wer mamit.
verse2:
Kaw luetena, giniti ma herani puonjoa;
Kaw tienda, mi ginidhi ka ma Ruoth chikoa.
verse3:
Kendo dwonda, mon'awer pile, kende ni Ruodha;
Kendo dhoga, kawe be, analand wachni pile.
verse4:
Kendo fedha, kata nok, kawgi, ok agomb moro.
Kaw riekona, ti kode gi ma idwaro Iwuon.
verse5:
Kaw parona; kik adwar gi ma ok idwaro In.
Kendo chunya, en mari, dak kanyo e chunya, Ruoth.

title: Bedi Mangima Kuoma
Ywaya Machiegni Buti Ruodha
verse1:
Ywaya machiegni buti, Ruodha; Agombo bet kodi Ywaya,
Ruaka gi hera mari, Adwaro kar yueyo.
verse2:
Ywaya machiegni, Jawar, ywaya, Kik iweya kenda;
Nabed mamor kabedo buti, kachandruok orumo.
verse3:
Ywaya gi roho mari, ywaya, Nyaka achal kodi;
Luoka, pwodha, kimiya bedo Maler ka'idwaro.

title: Diyie Dak Kod Yesu
verse1:
Diyie dak kod Yesu, mon'ibed maler pile?
Diyie wuoth kode e yo madiny koso?
Diyie mon'okaw tin'i duto kotin'ni?
Yiene ni mon'otelni.
verse2:
Diyie mon'ogonyi kendo iwinj wach mare?
Donge in'yo kuwe ma chiwruok kelo?
Ok diher mon'owari, kik ipodhi e keth?
Yiene ni mon'otelni.
verse3:
Diher yud kar bet e pinyruodhe malo koso?
Diher n'yo tekone mar loyo tem?
Idwaro tiyo ni Ruoth gi tekoni duto?
Yiene ni mon'otelni.

title: Aseweyo Tich Maricho
verse2:
Kata ji duto oriemba, Ji duto noweyo En;
Chuny marach owuondo pile, En kende e mageno.
Ka da herane bet koda, Kuyo ok donyal maka.
Ok danwan'mor e piny kae, Ka da onge herano.
verse3:
Yesu kende e moroma, Muche mon'orit chunya;
Eka tichne anamaki, Enopuonja kindane.
Pinywani otimo mudho; Chien'mudho nolal chutho,
Konya! mon'achungi chien'o E pinyruodhi mosiko.

title: Awaro Bedo Nyathi Yesu
verse1:
Adwaro bedo nyathi Yesu; Nyisa yo, nyisa yo;
Datim chikni duto, Jawarna, Konya tinende.
verse2:
Pith gi duon'mar piny odok nono, Mak Intie, mak Intie;
Anawe giduto ni Nyingi, Mwanduna ni ma.
verse3:
Kawito gik mantie e piny ka, Sud buta, sud buta;
Gik masiko duto ni kodi, Ma okonya ka.

title: Teko Nyasaye Orita
verse1:
Teko Nyasaye orita, Abed n't Yesu chuth;
Abed maler e pinyni kaluwo ndach Yesu.
verse2:
Teko Nyasaye orita, Atim gi modwaro;
Abed n'te malon', Moikre ni tich Ruoth.
verse3:
Teko Nyasaye orita, Apogra chuth kod piny;
Abed gi chuny mar Yesu-mamuol, man'on, maler.
verse4:
Teko Nyasaye orita, Abed n'te kende;
Abed n't Yesu koro, Kendo ma nyaka chien'

title: Asebayo Mabor Kodi
verse1:
Asebayo mabor kodi Ruodha, koro abironi,
Adwaro mondo abed e ritni, koro abironi.
verse2:
Aol gi piny kod richo mogundho ko'adwogo dala;
Ayie Jawar norwaka e kunde ko'aduogo dala.
verse3:
An'yo Jawar nomiya yweyo ko'adwogo dala;
Adwaro keto chunya e lwete ko'aduogo dala.
verse4:
Ayie tiyoni ka n'ma jachan ko'adwogo dala;
Adwaro nwan' n'ono mar Jawar ko'adwogo dala.
verse5:
Pakuru Ruoth, aneno Jawarna ko'adwogo dala;
Orito rwako jomolal ka an ko'adwogo dala.

title: Isedwaro Yueyo Kod Yie Momedore
verse1:
Isedwaro yuweyo kod yie momedore,
Isesayo gi chuny motur ngan'
Yuweyo ok niyud ngan'kata gweth malon',
Nyak isechiwori misango.
verse2:
Ber iwuoth gi Ruodhi e ler manie wachne,
To niyuwe e yo maber mar Ruoth,
Nyak itim chik Ruodhi mon'ibed maler chuth,
Gigi te nya'ichiw misango.
verse3:
Ok wanyal n'yo ngan'Gik ma Ruoth chiwonwa,
Kuom gwethgo ma wasekwayogo,
Ringrewa kod chunywa,
Oneg ochik chutho, Kendo wachiw duto misango.
verse4:
N' ma diwach hera mobiro oronwa,
Kendo chunywa nobed mamor ngan'
Mit mar wuoyo kode noromwa waduto,
Kwasechiwo duto misango.

title: Mana Kak' Abet Abironi
verse1:
Mana ka'abet abiro, ok anyal bet maber kenda,
Adwaro rembi moroma yie iwara kuom n'ononi.
verse2:
Mana ka'abet an'yo, Rembi kende emoroma,
Noluoka matar moloyo komiya genoi chutho.
verse3:
Mana ka'abet abiro,chunya mool ogomboi,
Ok anyal bet mabor kodi, Adwaro bet mari chutho.
verse4:
Chunya gi ngimana duto, Mondo oyud yuweyo kuomi,
'se bayo ma ase ol, Ayuweyo kuom hera mari.

title: Wuora ,Atang'oni Lueta
verse1:
Wuora, atan'ni lueta, In kendi kar konyruok;
Ka da iweya kenda ngan' An to dachik kanye?
verse2:
An koro ayie kuom Wuodi; Mon'an' tekoni;
Imiya gik marem koro, Mondo ipon'chunya.
verse3:
In Wuon genruok; an'yoi Kageno konyruokni;
Kik idaga, asayoi, Ayud ngima kuomi.

title: Yesu An Adwaro
verse1:
O Yesu, an adwaro Atini nyaka chieng`
Asayi bedi buta, Ruodha ma jakonya.
Ok analuor lwenj Satan ka In ibet buta;
Yo maber ok aweyo ka In itelona.
verse3:
O Yesu, isewacho duto molu ban',
Ka ma intie e duon'i Ginibedi bende.
To Yesu, an adwaro Atini nyaka chien'
Asayi konya pile, Ruodha ma Jawarna.

title: Weche Mag Mirima
verse1:
Weche mag mirima mondo Kik pusre a e dhowa;
Paro maber mon'ogen'i Ka pok giwuok e dhowa.
verse2:
Wach marach jawuok mapiyo, To gin gik maduwo chuny;
Gi maketho osiep kindwa, To weche mag mirima.
verse3:
Hera ler kendo olon', Kik wayie ketho osiep;
Nikech wach marach mwapuso; Ber mondo warit dhowa.

title: Otelona
verse1:
Otelona! Amor chutho, To Yesu e motelona;
Gima datim kama antie, To En Owuon otelona.
verse2:
Ka chunya lit, ka chunya yom, Ka yamo nego ji e piny;
Masira dak oketha ngan' Yesu Owuon otelona.
verse3:
Hapi oroma nyaka chien' Itieko nyisa yo maber;
To kata yo obet mabor, Yesu Iwuon itelona.
verse4:
Jachien odwaro wuondowa, Jopiny giweya kenda ka;
To n't maber moloyogi, Yesu owuon otelona.
verse5:
Ka tichna gik e pinywa ka, Abiro chopo e polo;
Ka tho obiro ok aluor, Yesu Owuon otelona.

title: Adwaro Bet Buti
verse1:
Adwaro bet buti, Nyasaye Wuora; Abed buti chutho, Yesu Ruodha
Ndalo duto abed buti Nyasaye Wuora; Asik buti pile Nyasaye Wuora.
verse2:
Achalo gi jawuoth e pinyni ka; Kar yueyo ongena, ler onge be;
To adwaro siko buti Nyasaye Wuora, Asik buti pile Nyasaye Wuora.
verse3:
Duto mimiyoa kuom n'ononi, Giywayo chunya chuth, abed buti;
Nyisa wan'o mari, en e ma mon'alu; Asik buti pile, Nyasaye Wuora.
verse4:
Kendo gi tekona nadend nyingi; In Lwandana, Ruodha, In warruokna;
Kata e masira, apadora kuomi, Asik buti pile, Nyasaye Wuora.
verse5:
Kochier a e liel chin'bironi, Adonj ka ma Intie, Nyasaye Wuora;
Nayud mor mochwere e dalani maber, Nabed buti pile, ma nyaka chien'

title: Paro Achiel Mamit
verse1:
Paro achiel mamit, Osiko e chunya;
Ndalo sudo machiegini, Ma nadonj e polo.
verse2:
E dala mar Wuora, Nitie udi man'ny;
Kom-duon'Nyasaye ni kanyono, En kar bet Yesu Ruoth.
verse3:
Ka tichna orumo, Masira gi kuyo;
Nadonj e dala mar Wuora, Nosidhna osimbo.

title: Onego abed gi Yesu
verse1:
Onego abed gi Yesu, Ok anyal wuotho kenda.
Ka Yesu obedo buta Anyalo yudo teko.
verse2:
Onego abed gi Yesu, Kuom Yie mara e chunya;
Wechene ohoyo chunya, Ka gimiya tekone.
verse3:
Onego abed gi Yesu, E ngimana duto te;
Kata an e temruok moro, kata e parruok moro.
verse4:
Onego abed gi Yesu E yorena duto te;
Eka an anyalo chopo E dala mosingonwa.

title: Ruoth Ni Koda E Yo Duto
Telna O yaye Ruoth Jehova
Yesu kotaya pile
verse1:
Yesu kotaya pile, Oritowa man'on;
An to kabedo bute, Onge gi manyalo luor.
Winji, machalo dwonde Malaika mawero,
Weche mabiro ira, Weche mamiya mor.

title: Be Yesu ling
verse1:
Be Yesu lin'ka chunya otur, Kuom dwaro mor kata wer;
Saa ma tin'tura parruok be ola, ka wuoth bedo maolo chuny?
verse2:
Be Yesu lin'ka chunya opon'kod buok be luoro mathoth;
Kodiechien'rumo kotieno chopo, bende obedo machiegni?
verse3:
Be Yesu lin'saa ma tem matek asekedogo motama;
Ka chunya kuyo hoch be ongena, kata pi wan' chwer malit?
verse4:
Be Yesu lin'ka tho pogoa gosiepna mahero chuth;
Ka chunya kuyo kachiegni gi tho, be olin'ma ok onena?

title: Ka Yembe Mag Kuyo Luora
verse1:
Ka yembe mag kuyo luora, gipandona yo mar ngima;
Chunya ok nobed gi luoro, an'yo n' matayoa.
verse2:
