Pile ka'apaka tuoma, kaneno luendni mag chandruok;
Luoro kod kiawa ongena, an'yo n' matayoa.
verse3:
Kata tem birona pile, kata nam bed marach nade;
To nyaka anagow loka, An'yo n' matayoa.
verse4:
Hera Jawar pod telona, En e monyisa yo maber;
Nagene nyaka atiek wuodha, An'yo n' matayoa.

title: Jawar Telna Kik Alal
verse1:
Jawar telna kik alal (ni kik alal), Telna mos e yo duto( e yo duto);
An gi kue ka an buti (ka an buti), Dagomb bet e herani (e herani).
verse2:
In e kar bwok mar chunya (kuwe mar chunya), Ka yamo maduon'kudho (Yamo kudho);
An gi kuwe ka in buta (ka in buta), An gi geno kuomi Ruoth (geno kuomi).
verse3:
Jawar telna pile ka (telna pile), Ka yamo osekadho (yamo kadho);
Telna nyaka piny manyien (Ruodha telna), Kama piwan'a noywe (Wan'a noywe).

title: Ka Chandruok Mar Piny Ochopo
verse1:
Ka chandruok mar piny ochopo, Lweny mager e piny gi nam,
Anadwar kar pondo mara, e bwo tipo lwet Nyasaye.
verse2:
Kata da okelna chandruok, pod named geno polo,
Ruoth okumo jomohero, konyisogi yo maber.
verse3:
Ka wasika dwaro hinya, Ka Satan dwaro loya,
Ruoth nolok gima dihinya, Obedna mor mochwere.
verse4:
Ka atin' msalapa, Ka aneno chandruok e piny,
Yesu e ma rito chunya, ok noweya mon'alal.

title: Kwonde Duto Motelona
verse1:
Kwonde duto motelona, Anadhi nikech agene;
Aparo kaka nothona, Rembe nochwer e Kalwari.
verse2:
An amor kawinjo chikne; Amor chutho kotelona;
To chunya mor kuom dwarone, Kaparo thone Kalwari.
verse3:
Adhiyo nyime mak aluor, Amor kuom Kristo, Jawarna;
Ageno neno Osiepna, Yesu mothona Kalwari.

title: In Wang Yorwa
verse1:
In wan'orwa; wabironi Kwaringo keth gi tho;
Kendo n' modwaro wuoro Nya'odware kuomi.
verse2:
In Adiera; Wachni kende Nyalo miwa rieko;
Puonj madieri oa kuomi, In ma Japwodh chunywa.
verse3:
In ngimawa; liel ma notur Ohulo tekoni;
Tho kata liel ok anonyal Jogo magenoi.
verse4:
In yo, Adiera, gi Ngima; Puonjwa wan' yorno;
Konywa warit adierano, Miwa ngimani, Ruoth.

title: Yesu Onindo E Jasi
verse1:
Yesu onindo e jasi, Kokadho nam Galili;
Ahiti maduon'to okudho, Pi nam gingore malich.
Jopuonjre chiewe gi luoro;'uoth ok idew kwatho?`
Eka Yesu nokwero apaka, Nochiko yembe gilin'
verse2:
Yesu achandora tinde, Apaka ni e chunya;
Temruok to obiro ka yamo, Ayiengini, Ruoth konya.
Kethruok awinjo kohewa, Chunya odhier chutho,
To Ruoth Yesu bi piyo, asayi; Bi sira gi tekoni.
verse3:
Ruodha, chunya koro kuwe mos, Chandruok osekadhona;
Kuwe mari koro ni e chunya, Kuom teko mar wachni, Ruoth.
Bed koda pile, Jawarna, Kik iweya kenda ngan'
Eka danyal chopo ka maner cha, Abed kodi nyaka chien'

title: Yesu Obiro Ka Kendo
verse1:
Yesu obiro ka kendo, Yesu ma notho Kalwari;
Obiro omo jo moyie, Mondo gidhi polo.
verse2:
Waneno tim man'ny e piny Mapuonjowa wach birone;
Chien'o obiro mana ru Ma wanadhi polo.
verse3:
Ndalo man'ny to lweny nitie; To pinje ok noyudi kuwe;
Nyaka Jawarwa wi'e piny, Mon'oterwa polo.
verse4:
Eka e piny maber, manyien, Wanabedi ma nyaka chien'
Ok wanachak waketh kendo, To wanamor pile.

title: Wuoth Pod Odong Marom Nade
verse1:
Wuoth pod odon'marom nade? Jarit odwoko wach kama;
`Otieno chiegini rumo, Piny biro mana ru.`
Kik koro ibed gi kuyo, Iteg wan' ku midhiye,
Nya'idonje pinyruodh Nyasaye, Kar ler ma nyaka chien'
verse3:
Napenjo kendo ka'obet; Piny ngima nodwoka kama;
"Wuoth me pinyni dwaro rumo, Waki ma nyaka chien'"
Kik koro wabed gi kuyo, Ranyisi n'ny mayangonwa,
Ni chwech duto rito winjo Dwond Ruodhwa kobiro.
verse4:
Ok bor koro nyaka thurwa! Wachni hoyo chunywa e yo;
Ogolo kuyo gi pi wan' Omiyo chunywa kuwe.
Kik koro wabed gi kuyo, Podi matin to wanarom,
E kar mor chutho mochwere, E dala mar Wuonwa.

title: Gin Weche Mamit
verse1:
Gin weche mamit ma Jakristo owinjo, Kowuotho e piny marachni;
Ndalo don'matin nyaka Ruoth Yesu nobi, Kobiro chungo pinyruodhe.
verse2:
Liete ka ma koro Jokristo nindoe, Noyawre malach e chien'o;
Ji duto maler ma notho kageno Ruoth, Nochier gi ngima mochwere.
verse3:
Pogruok ok nobedi kucha e piny manyien, Ji nodag kuro nyaka chien'
Mowar a tun'piny duto nobedi kuro, Ka gipako Ruoth gi wende.
verse4:
Wawer "Alleluya" kwadendo Ruoth Yesu; Wabed jo madieri chutho;
Kwarito gi kinda nyaka Ruodhwa nobi, Nosidhnwa osimbo maber.

title: Jo Maler Duto Rituru
verse1:
Jo maler duto rituru teko polo koro, Yiengni;
Mokuru techeu duto, kurito biro mar ruodhwa.
verse2:
Landuru wach kwonde duto,Kunyiso ji wach mar warruok;
Kuom jathieth gi hera mare, kod teko mar weyo richo.
verse3:
Pinje Ruodhi biro kadho; Pinyruodhe oduon'gilala;
Landuru wach nguono mare, Ka ndalogi pok okadho.
verse4:
Ogend pinyni to lal nono, kamirima pon' chunygi;
Kristo dwaro biro piyo, Mondo pinyruodhe ochungi.
verse5:
Jo maricho to biuru, Mondo Kristo luoknu richo;
Returu, ukaw n'onone, ndalo koro chiegni rumo.

title: Gouru Bu, Goyeuru Matek
verse1:
Gouru bu, goyeuru matek:
Yesu obiro kendo!
Jiwuru chunyu, jowuoth, weruru;
Yesu obiro kendo!
verse2:
Landuru wachno e gode gi pap:
Yesu obiro kendo!
Nobi gi duon' Nyarombo ma notho;
Yesu obiro kendo!
verse3:
Landuru wachni e pinje duto:
Yesu obiro kendo!
Dho wedhe duto mon'owinj wachni:
Yesu obiro kendo!

title: Chieng no Odwaro Yawore
verse1:
Chien'o maduon'to nobinwa piyo, mar biro Yesu;
Nobi ni mondo oter nyithinde e utgi malo.
verse2:
Wach mar injili nolandre piyo ni dhoudi te;
Eka Ruoth Yesu Kristo noduogi, mi bu noyuagi .
verse3:
Jopolo duto nokowe bende e boche polo;
Ruodhwa nobi tero jo makare kama tho onge.
verse4:
Jo ma wahero to koro nindo; to wananere;
Ok wanayuagi e pinyruodh polo, wanamor kende.

title: Singruok Maber Ngang
Ok Wangeyo Saa Ma Nobie
verse1:
Ok wangeyo saa ma nobie, ka'okinyi, ka'odhiambo,
Di po kobiro ka piny chido, kata saa ma piny dwaro ru.
Ochikowa mondo warite, kik wawe techewa otho,
Mondo ka obiro oyudwa wan duto kwarito Ruodhwa.

Wa  rito Ruodhwa; ( warito kendo wakiyo Ruodhwa;)
Warito Ruodhwa; ( warito kendo wakiyo Ruodhwa;)
Warito Ruodhwa; Warito kendo wakiyo Ruoth.
verse2:
Aparo n'onone maduon'ngan' ma nomiye thonwa e yath,
Koweyo duon'e polo malo, mon'otho ni jo maricho.
An'yo ka Ruodhwa dimor ngan'ka  jogo ma notho nigi mor,
Ka gikiyo duok Ruodhwa, ka giduto rite pile.
verse3:
Ruoth Yesu, jawarna mohera, In'yo kaheri adier;
Ageno naneni gi wan' ka iniruaka e polo.
Kibiro kaka jan'd bura ni jogo maringo wan',
An to anamosi, Osiepna; An to arito bironi.

title: Mor Ni Jopiny
verse1:
Mor ni jopiny Ruoth noduogi! Piny mon'oruak Ruodhe,
To ji losne chunygi chutho;Polo gi piny pake, polo gi piny pake,
Polo gi piny pako Ruodhwa. (Polo gi piny pake).
verse3:
Obiro loyo piny gi kuwe, To ogend piny non',
Duon'e madier gi loch mokuwe, Gi herane maduon' Gi herane maduon'
Gi herano maduon'mar Ruoth. (Gi herane maduon'.

title: Dong Iikri Rono Ni Ruoth
verse1:
Dong iikri romo ni Ruoth kobiro, kobiro?
Dong iikri romo ni Ruoth kobiro, kobiro?
Ochiegni biro! Ochiegni biro!
Ikri mar romo ni Ruoth kobiro.
verse2:
Ni mon'une ka teche liel kobiro, kobiro;
Ni mon'une ka teche liel kobiro, kobiro.
Nobi mapiyo! Nobi mapiyo!
Ikri mar romo ni Ruoth kobiro.
verse3:
Duto wadhi warom ni Ruoth kobiro, kobiro;
Duto wadhi warom ni Ruoth kobiro, kobiro.
Nobi adieri! Nobi adieri!
Wadhi warom ni Ruodhwa kobiro.
verse4:
Wanawerne "Alleluya" kobiro, kobiro;
Wanawerne "Alleluya" kobiro, kobiro.
Obiro biro! Obiro biro! 
Wanawer wende pak ka Ruoth biro.

title: Ne Obiro E Koth Polo
verse2:
Ji duto bende nonene, Birone to lich ni gi,
Manochaye, ma nogure, Ka notho e Kalwari.
Giniyuagi, Ka gineno duon'mar Ruoth.
verse4:
Chien'Kristo nokelnwa warruok, Koro wanadhi polo.
Ji mochier, gi ji molokre, Ma nodhur mathoth ka lum.
Alleluya! Chien'o tho gi tuo norum.
verse5:
Ee wariti! Ruodhwa Yesu; Chunywa tinde gomboi.
Mondo wan duto waikre, Ka wakiyo bironi.
Kik wadeki, Yesu Ruodhwa mon'ibi.

title: Di Po Ka Nobed Saa
verse1:
Di po ka nobed saa ma wan'chien'opilre,
Kama ler oketho mudho mar otieno,
Ma Yesu nobi koa polo gi duon'e
Ni mon'okaw joge e piny.
verse2:
Koso odiechien' koso ka piny oyuso, koso odiewuor,
Ma mudho chien'noturnwa, kod lerno malich;
Ma norieny a e polo,
Ka Ruoth Yesu omo joge.
verse3:
Ogandane duto nokogi, Hosana! Malaika,
To gi joge maler duto, ka Malaika kowe e boche polo,
Ka Ruoth Yesu omo joge.
verse4:
Nikech wan wakiya ndalo ma nobie,
Onego warit chunywa mondo waikre,
Chien'o kik powa, kendo bura kik lowa,
Ka Ruoth Yesu omo joge.

title: Yesu Nobi Kendo
verse2:
Piny noyiengni kendo, polo noa kare,
Mi jo mak ler nobed nade e ndalono maduon'
Gionge kar ringo ka piny nobed malich,
Mirimb Nyasaye nonere ka n'ono oserumo.

title: Keyo Mar Pinyni
verse1:
Keyo mar pinyni to koro chiegini;
Ruoth dwaro jokeyo ni mondo gibi,
Kendo gika chambe e puothe duto,
Mon'okan e deche ka Ruodhwa biro.
verse2:
Ndalono mochwere, ma pi wan'onge,
Okayo machiegni, ochiegni koro;
To yamo mar richo dwaro keyo cham,
Returu ukawe, pod kinde nitie.

title: Chieng Ma Bu Mar Nyasachwa Noyuagi
verse1:
Chien'ma bu mar Nyasachwa noyuagi e ndalo giko,
Chien'o e ma piny noyawre, nyaka chien'
Chien'o jo mowar nochokre e dho wadh aoch ngima.
Ka iluongo nying jo maler nabedie!

title: Ruodha Ok Agomb Moko
Ruodhwa Yesu Oseluongowa
verse1:
Ruodhwa Yesu oseluongowa, Mondo wachop e kiserane;
Wan to wanabed nade chien'o, Ka Ruodhwa biro?
verse2:
Enoruake gi duon'mar polo, 'simbo mar duon'e mar locho;
Osimb kudho ok nonen kendo, Ka Ruodhwa biro.
verse3:
Ji man gi lep kisera nomor, Nikech noruakgi e kisera;
Wan johawi ka Ruoth noyienwa, Ka Ruodhwa biro.
verse4:
Ji modagi noyuagi chien'o, Kiriembogi a e kisera;
Nobed malich miwuoro chien'o, Ka Ruodhwa biro.
verse5:
Ruoth mondo imiwa n'ononi, Wan duto, jogi maritoi;
Mondo kik waluor ka waneni, Kiwiro,Ruodhwa.

title: Ka Jabura Nong ad Buchwa
verse1:
Ka Jabura non'd buchwa, E ngima kata e tho,
Enokwanwa nade chien'o, Jo maler koso joketh?
verse2:
Wanawinj weche kowacho, "Jatich maber, makare,"
Koso enokwerwa chutho, "In Jaricho moloyo?"
verse3:
Dak wawinj dwonde kosayo, "Donji e n'ono mara."
Koso wanabed kwadeko, nyaka bura nolowa?

title: Ndalo Maduong Biro
verse1:
Ndalo maduon'biro ochiegni koro, ndalono mar biro Ruoth Yesu,
Kama Ruoth nopog joge dhiyo korachich, Dongi iikri ni ndalo nogo?
verse2:
Ndalo maler biro ochiegni koro, ndalono mar biro Ruoth Yesu;
To lerne nobi ni jogo mohero Jawargi, dong iikri ni ndalo nogo?
verse3:
Ndalo malich biro ochiegni koro , ndalono mar biro Ruoth Yesu,
Ka nowach ni joricho "Auru ok an'u", dong iikri ni ndalo nogo?

title: Koro Kawuono Ruodhwa Man E Polo
verse1:
Koro kawuono, Ruodhwa man e polo, oseyawo buge bura;
Onono paro, weche, timbe, Kata richo, kata ber.
verse2:
Tich yandi ochaki kuom jo monindo; To ndalo koro chiegini,
Ma enononwa, jo mangima; To buchwa nobed nade?
verse3:
Kitap Nyasachwa nonyis weche duto; E ma Jan'd bura nosom;
Kaka non'd bura e saano, Nosiki ma nyaka chien'

title: Ok Wangeyo Saa
verse1:
Ok wan'yo saa ka ma Ruodhwa noduogi,
Ranyisi man'ny e ma koro waneno;
Wan'yo nobi, En owuon e mowacho,
To ok wan'yo saa.

title: Ka Tichwa Oseruma
verse1:
Ka tichwa oserumo, ka wasetieko n'ewa;
Mi nyithindi, yueyoni, nyaka chien' Wuonwa.
verse2:
Kwasetieko lwenjewa, koseneg jasikwa;
Eka wanayud kuomi, kuwe ma nyaka chien'
verse3:
Ka mudho me piny norum, ka ndalo Ruodhwa noru;
Mondo wane chien'mari, Ler ma nyaka chien'
verse4:
Chien'ma chunywa noyud mor, nikech kuyo orumo;
Ywe pi wan'a, miwa mor, Mor ma nyaka chien'
verse5:
Ka ji timonwa malit, Mi watim machal Yesu;
Puonjwa herani maler, Hera mochwere.

title: Ka Yesu Ochoko Ji Duto
verse1:
Ka Yesu ochoko ji duto, kokelogi duto nyime;
Eka wanabedi manade, Kwachokore winjo buchwa?
verse2:
Wanawinj dwond Yesu Jawarwa, kowacho:
"Biuru ira;" Koso wanaluor moloyo, kowacho: "Auru kuoma?"
verse3:
Nomor ka oneno nyithinde, moseruako nanga maler;
To ginisiki gi Jawargi, enobedi Ruodhgi maber.
verse4:
Koro wanarit Yesu Kristo, kwaiko chunywa wan duto;
Kobiro noyiewa ni rombe, ok nowitwa oko ka diek.
verse5:
Ber waritre kwakiyo Ruodhwa, teche mondo siki kaliel;
Ka wuodhwa e pinyni orumo, wamor gi Ruodhwa nyaka chien'

title: Ka Boche Polo Oyawo E Wi Gode
verse1:
Ka watimo marach ka wakia ni wan dhano matho,
Ka waweyo chik mag n'ono kwatemo bedo maber,
N'onone mar kuwe noumwa, Richowa mag ndalogi,
Ka tich matek oserumo, Ka rondo oserumo.
verse2:
Ka rondo oseyawore wanan' osiepewa,
Kaka wuonwa bende on'yo nyithinde duto te;
Ka ndalo maduon'o biro, koa malo yor ugwe,
E chunywa duto warito, Nyaka rondo rum chutho.

title: Anane Wang Yesu Kristo
verse1:
Anane wan'Yesu Kristo, Kobi'eboche polo;
Nabedi mamor moloyo Ka Yesu owi'e piny.
verse2:
An to pok aneno Yesu, To ayiee gi chunya;
Chien'ofwenyore e polo, Ananene ka'obet.
verse3:
Pinyni orachna moloyo, nikech tho gi tuo nitie;
Anamor kaneno Yesu, Ok nane chandruok kendo.
verse4:
Yesu Kristo en Jan'ono, Nosetho ni ji duto;
Mondo n' moseyie kuome Kik olal ma nyaka chien'

title: Wanachokre E Aora
verse1:
Wanachokre e aora? Ka ma nitie pi ngima,
Pi mamit mawuok e Lwanda, E kar kom duong mar Nyasaye.
verse2:
Ka wawuotho but aora, E pinyruoth mar Nyasachwa,
Wanabed kwalemo pile, Wanadend nyinge pile.
verse3:
To ka pok wachopo kanyo, Wanawe tin'a duto;
Much Nyasaye nomi chunywa kuwe, Wanayud osimb locho.
verse4:
E dho aoch pi mar ngima, Jawarwa oritowa;
Nyaka chien'ok wanapogre, Wanapak nyinge gi wer.
verse5:
Aora odon'machiegni, Eka wuodhewa norum;
Eka wanabed mamor chuth, Wanayud kuwe nyaka chien'

title: Ka Tichna Oserumo
verse1:
Ka tichna oserumo kendo ayudo warruok,
Kaseruakora gi kido ma ok tow,
Anan' Jawarna kaseidho loka kocha,
En e n' ma nadwar neno mokwongo.
verse2:
Anayud mor e chunya ka aneno kwonde bet,
Ma Ruodhwa oiko ni joge maler;
Anapak Ruoth Jawarna kuom n'onone gi hera,
Moyie mondo ayud kar bet e polo.
verse3:
Kendo jogo ma notho ka gigeno Yesu Ruoth,
Ananegi kendo kuro e polo;
To kasechopo malo kanyo, dala mar Nyasaye,
Mokwongo adwaro neno Jawarna.
verse4:
Anadonji e dhorangach mar dala Nyasachwa,
Kuyo kata pi wan'onge kanyo ngan'
Anawer wend locho kaachiel gi jo mowar duto,
To agombo chutho neno wan'Jawar.

title: Dalawa Man Malo
verse1:
Waluwo yorno mar msalaba, kwadhiyo e polo;
Ok nwaluor maricho mogundho, ka Wuonwa ritowa.
verse2:
Waluwo yorno mar msalaba; Yesu osetelo;
Wanawuothi e ndach jatendwa, nyaka dhowath mar kuwe.
verse3:
Waluwo yorno mar msalaba, kata yo rach nade;
Luet Jawarwa notelnwa maber nyaka wachop ire.

title: Ndalo Duto Ma An E Piny
verse1:
Ndalo duto ma an e piny, Agombo dhi polo,
Kanyo ma Yesu losona; Adwaro dak kode.
verse2:
Pod wabedo jowuoth e piny, Tichwa to pok ogik;
Mar lando wach mar Injili Kuom Yesu ma Jawar.
verse3:
Ndalo matin mi wanadhi Kar hawi mochwere;
Wabiro neno wan'Wuonwa Kod wan'Yesu Ruodhwa.
verse4:
Chunya opon'gi mor chutho Kaparo kanyono;
Pinyni ok tero chunya ngan' Agombo dhi kuno.

title: Ji Noyud Mor Ka Tich Orumo
verse1:
Ji noyud mor ka tich orumo, ka jo keyo biro gi cham
Ma gikelo ni Ruoth maduon' E Jerusalem Manyien.
verse2:
Wanawer wende mamit chien'o, wanayud  mor ngan'e chunywa,
Kwadendo Ruodhwa nyaka chien'E Jerusalem Manyien.
verse3:
Jo keyo noyudi mor maduon' kod kwonde bet ma nyaka chien'
Yesu Ruoth oseloso E Jerusalem Manyien.

title: Nitie Piny Moro Maber Chutho
verse2:
Wanawer e polo nyaka chien' Wer mamit mar jogo molocho;
Kendo chunywa ok none kuyo, Kata chandruok moro nyaka chien'
verse3:
Ruoth Nyasachwa on'on gilala Wagoyone erokamano,
Nikech wuode ma nochiwonwa, To gi gwethne mosemiyowa.

title: Adwaro Bedo But Pi Ngima
verse1:
Adwaro bedo but pi ngima, Yesu e pi ngima,
Oritowa mondo oruakwa kanyono ma Entie.
verse2:
Kwaol ka wawuotho e wan'o, owinjore wayue,
Ka ma nitie pigno mar ngima, Manyalo miwa mor.
verse3:
Ka riyo loyi, bi ir Yesu, eka riyo norum;
Yesu Owuon e pi ngima, modhe mondo ikwo.

title: E Pinyno Maber Manyien
verse1:
E pinyno maber manyien, Nitie dala maler;
Nosiki ma nyaka chien' Kendo mudho onge.
verse2:
Dhorangeye mag lulu, E dalano maler;
Yorene mag dhahabu, Kendo mudho onge.
verse3:
Dhorangeyene ok lor, E dalano maler;
Aoch ngima mol kanyo, Kendo mudho onge.
verse4:
Kanyo ok gidwar wan'chien' E dalano maler;
To Nyarombo En lerne, Kendo mudho onge.

title: Ka Tichna Rumo
verse1:
Ka tichna rumo, masiche kogik, Bende kachopo e polo malo;
Bedo but Yesu Jahera maduon'Nobedi morna mamit mosiko.
verse2:
Chien'chopo polo gi joge duto, Nikech mirembe mawenwa richo;
Kulri nyim Yesu, gi kom mar Nyasaye, Nobedi morna mamit mochwere.
verse3:
Wanane Jokristo moseko tho, Wuone gi mine gowetewa be;
Kata kamano da Kristo paka, Chunya nobedi mamor moloyo.

title: Wawinjo Mar Dala Maler
verse2:
Kanyo richo onge chutho, Masira gi temruok bende;
Gi ma dimi chunywa kuyo Onge kuro dala Nyasaye.
Ji nobed gi chuny mar hera, Giniyud osimb dhahabu,
Bende lewni marachere, Ma Yesu norwakgo joge.
verse4:
Mago ma wan'pok oneno, yit bende to pok owinjo,
Ma chuny dhano pok oparo, Nyasaye oloso ni joge.
Watimuru kinda koro, nyaka chien'ma Yesu nobi;
Wadonji e pinyno maber, Wadag kod Yesu nyaka chien'

title: Pinyni Ok Thurwa Mwageno
verse4:
Chunya, kuwe mos! Ruoth on'yo,
Ndalo ma iniyud yueyo;
E piny ka mon'atim chikne,
Ka pod arito ndalono,
Ka pod arito ndalono.

title: Un Jowuoth To Udhi Kanye
verse1:
Un jowuoth, to udhi kanye? Un maneno nyima ka.
Wan wadhiyo dala Ruodhwa, Wan wawuotho ku mabor.
Wan wadhiyo ku mabor, to Wan wadhi ka piny moloyo;
Wan wadhiyo piny mar Ruodhwa, Piny moloyo pinje te.
verse2:
Nyiswa gi mudwaro yudo, Kusetundo piny maber.
Wanayudi gik moloyo, Yesu madhi miyowa.
Wanane Jakonywa kucha, Gi Nyasaye to wanabedi;
Nyaka chien'to wanasiki, Kwasetundo piny maber.
verse3:
Un jowuoth to un uyie Mondo wan wadhi kodu?
Ee, biuru, kik udeki, Ber udhi kachiel kodwa.
Biuru, to kik uwewa, Yesu e moruako duto;
Enoyie mondo udonji, Mon'usiki piny maber.

title: Anarwak Osimb Dhahabu
verse1:
Anarwak Osimb dhahabu e polo, Nawe tin'a duto piny kadhi polo;
Karwako lep locho anawer sigana, Mar Ruoth manon'ewa kadhi polo.
verse2:
Mudho duto enorum kadhi polo, Eka nane ler achien kadhi polo;
Ka ler mar polo rieny komenyo wan'yora, Kawuotho elerno kadhi polo.
verse3:
Anane wan'Jawarna kadhi polo, Nawer n'ono mar Jawar kadhi polo;
Kachungo e nyime, anapake gi mor, Nabed kode pile kadhi polo.

title: Asewinjo kuom piny
verse1:
Asewinjo kuom piny man mabor loka nam,
En kar dak maber mar jo mo war;
Yesu e moloso udi mag dalano,
En piny ma ok wanabed moti.
verse2:
E dalano maber ma ok wanalalie,
Wanabedi gi mor gi lala;
Wanapak Ruoth Yesu e piny Ruoth mochwere,
Piny ma ok wanathoe kendo.
verse3:
Ka tichwa orumo kwaseyudo'imbo,
Masiche ok nobedie kendo;
Yuak gi tem norum chuth, wanawer gi jogo,
Mosekwongonwa dhiyo kuno.

title: Aparo koro kuom pinyno maber
verse1:
Aparo koro kuom pinyno maber, Piny maber, maber ngan'
En kar yuweyo maber ban'chandruok duto.
Piny maber kendo mar kuwe,
En piny ma nosingi chon ni jogo maler.
Giniyue kuom chandruok duto,
Kama cham kod olembe nomi chunywa mor.
verse2:
Anawer wende mag hera kanyo,
Piny maber, maber ngan'
Anapak Jawarna gi wende mamit
Piny maber kendo mar kuwe,
Wanawinj thumbe mayuak mamit e polo;
Duonde duoko mamit kendo
Ka jomalaika maler nower gi mor,
E pinyno maber ngan'
verse3:
Koro aneno kar dak mepolo,
Piny maber, maber ngan'
Piny maber kendo mar kuwe,
Osiepe ma jowuodha koro chiegni wuok,
Asewinjo duondgi koro;
Nikech yie nigi teko mar fwenyo weche;
Mag pinyno maber ngan'

title: E Loka Nam
verse1:
E loka nam e dho wadh kuwe Kama richo duto norum ;
Kama chandruok ok nobedie Tiende mool noyud yweyo.
verse2:
Onge paro gik mokadho Chunya mool noyud teko;
Pi wan'a ok nochwer kendo Wenge mool none Jawar.
verse3:
E loka nam kar kuwe gi mor Yesu luongo nyithinde te;
E loka nam parruok norum Malaika wero wend ruak.

title: Ageno Wanarom
verse1:
Ageno wanarom e polo, E tiend yadh ngima maber;
Ageno wanapak jawarwa; kuom n'uono mar warowa.
verse2:
Ageno wanarom e polo, kwaluoro kom duon'Nyasaye;
Ageno bedo gi jomowar, kwapako hera Jawar.
verse3:
Ageno wanarom e polo, katichna me piny rumo;
Ageno wanamosre gi mor, E wath marieny mochwere.

title: Ka Wadhi E Polo
verse1:
Ka wawuotho kawachiko polo Bor polo noum lwasi;
To ka ndalo mad wuoth norum, Tipo kod kuyo norum.
verse2:
Wabeduru jomadieri Kwatiyo kendo gene;
To ban'kinde matin kende Ngimani mar dhier norum.
verse3:
To michno moseikonwa Wanamor kwaneno Ruoth;
Ka dhoranga polo yawnwa Wanalu yor dhahabu.

title: Ase cho'e piny mar mwandu
verse1:
Ase cho'e piny mar mwandu, Ma pithne nwan're nono;
Kawuono chien'orieny maler, Manyiso ler manyaka chien'
verse2:
Jawar biro wuotho koda, Bende sawo wachamo ngan'
Otelona mos kod luete, Ni kech ma e polo maler.
verse3:
Mo man'e n'r owirago, ma tikne a e yadh ngima,
Ma thiepege ok nyal nur ngan' Ma'ch ngima molie pile.
verse4:
Yamb imbo ma biro ira, Dwond wer mamit okelona,
Kaka malaika maler wero wer mamit mar warruok.

title: Nitie ber Kwonde Duto
Nyasaye Nomiyo Adam Jakony
verse1:
Nyasaye nomiyo Adam Jakony e puoth Eden;
To pod oyie ni dhano Mon'okonyre kama.
verse2:
Nikech wachni maduon'to dichwo nowe jonyuol;
Ni mon'odag gi chiege; Ginibedi kachiel.
verse3:
Yesu nohero joge Nyaka nochiwore;
Chwo mondo giher mondgi gi hera ma kama.
verse4:
Kanisa to owinjo Weche duto mag Ruoth;
Ka mon winjo chwogi, Winjruok nitie maber.
verse5:
Muya maler, wasayi Bedi machiegini;
Konyruok moro to onge mak In mibet kodwa.

title: Wamor Kwaromo Kod Osiepe
Nindo Kuom Yesu
verse1:
Nindo kuom Yesu! En hawi!
Ka n'to tho kogeno Ruoth;
Okuwe mos kanyo e i liel,
Wasigu ok nonyale ngan'
verse2:
Nindo kuom Yesu! Ma ber ngan'
Onge kuyo kata pi wan'
Onindo mos nyaka chien'o,
Ma dwond Ruoth Yesu nochiere.
verse3:
Nindo kuom Yesu! Johawi!
Jogo ma nochier ndalono;
Ginine duon'mar Ruoth polo,
Kobiro omo jo maler.
verse4:
Nindo kuom Yesu! Ginichier!
Ka tun'machien obiro kok;
Giniyiech liete ndalono,
Ginuyud ngima mosiko.

title: Yesu Rembi Ma Nosechwer
verse1:
Yesu, rembi ma nosechwer Maluoko richona,
Nochwer mondo ayud warruok, Koa e n'ti, Ruoth.
verse2:
Abedo chwech manyien koro,
Kuom remono maler;
Dhano machon otho koro,
Angima kuom Yesu.
verse3:
Awuotho gi ngima manyien,
Mar loyo piny gi keth;
Chunya ler bende wuodha ler,
Ka Kristo dak koda.
verse4:
N'ono miwuoro mar Jawar,
Kopwodha gi rembe;
Yesu ma nothona e yath,
En Ruodh chunya koro.

title: Yesu Wabiro Iri
verse1:
Yesu wabiro iri tinende,
Wakulore nyimi, bi gwedhwa koro.
verse2:
Wayuak e nyimi, wenwa kethowa;
Iluokwa gi rembi, Rembi ma nochwer.
verse3:
Koro wanawe kitwa maricho;
To kit Yesu Kristo wamako tinde.
verse4:
Dwond Muya Maler, wuoyo e chunywa;
Onego wawinje ni mon'ogwedhwa.
verse5:
Waheri, wageni, Nyarombo motho;
Wapaki, wadendi, Amin, gi Amin.

title: Ruodha Dak Ipogna Kuon Mar Ngima
Yesu Ruoth Nisethona
verse4:
Chien'o ma niwir e piny, Ka aseloyo richo,
Nadhi kodi e polo, Ananeni e kom duon'
Yesu, In e Lwandana, Anageni nyaka chien'

title: Winjuru Tinde Dwond Jakwath
verse1:
Winjuru tinde dwond Jakwath, Otieko dhi e thim malich;
Ni mon'oluong rombe molal; Chunye nomor konwan'gi.
verse2:
Koro giyuak marach e thim, To gik maricho ni kuno;
N' ma nodhi konyo Jakwath Ni mon'omany duto molal?
verse3:
Yesu noa polo malo, Nochandore marach e piny;
Rembe nochwer mon'owarwa, Wan rombe Yesu molal.
verse4:
Rombe mamagi pod olal, Ma pok odonjo e kwedhe;
Winjuru wach Yesu tinde, "Dhiuru manyo rombega."

title: Wabiro Iri Yesu
verse1:
Wabiro iri, Yesu, Kwakelo nyithindwa,
Ni mon'igwedhgi koro, Ka podi gitindo.
verse2:
Dwakwayi an', Ruodhwa, Mone'igwedhgi go?
Wasayi mon'iritgi Kuom temruok ma nie piny.
verse3:
Ok dak wakwayi mwandu, mamayo chuny ji kuwe;
To migi chuny mageno gikeni mar polo.
verse4:
To rieko moa malo, bende paro maler,
Gi chuny mamuol mokonyo Jogo machandore.
verse5:
Teko mar lwenje pinyni, wasayi, migi, Ruoth;
Mondo gikedi pile, Satan kik ologi.

title: Hera Mamiyowa Mor
verse1:
Hera mamiyowa mor, Hera maloso chuny,
Omiyowa bedo man'on; Gi ji duto pile.
verse2:
E piny ka nitie kuyo, Chandruok, gi keth, gi tho;
Chuny mar hera nyalo hoyo, Jo madwaro konyruok.
verse3:
Chien'koduogo e pinyni, Mond oterwa polo;
Wanawer kuno nyaka chien' Hera mar Ruoth Yesu.

title: An Amor Ngang
verse2:
Ka wiya wil kendo ka aruenyo,
Pod ohera kendo oluonga;
To anaduog ir Ruoth Jakonya,
Kahingo ka Yesu oheroa.
verse3:
Hera e momiye tho Kalwari,
Hera e momiye manyowa ka;
Chien'moro wanawer wer e polo,
Kaka ne Yesu ohero jopiny.

title: Yesu In Osiep Nyithindo
verse1:
Yesu, In Osiep nyithindo, Bedi Osiepna;
Mak lueta, ibedi koda Kawuotho.
verse2:
Puonja mon'atim makare, To ayom chutho;
Ne In nyathi, e momiyo In'yo.
verse3:
Taya pile, Yesu Kristo, To in'yo yo;
An akia, an afuwo; Naruenyo.
verse4:
Bedi koda, kik iweya, In e Osiepna;
Anadwari pile pile Nyaka chien'

title: Anayie Ruoth Yesu Koro
verse1:
An ayie Ruoth Yesu koro, An ayiee gi chunya;
Osewacho e wach mare mondo nyithindo dhine.
verse2:
Anadhi ka ma odwaro, Analu ban' pile.
Ka'an nyathi, ee anyalo, To Yesu otelona.
verse3:
Entie pile mon'okonya, Kik Satani oloya;
Ka abedo bute pile, Anyalo timo maber.

title: Yesu Ma Ni Malo
verse1:
Yesu ma ni malo winj alamwa ka,
Ka wakulore nyimi, Ka wapakoi.
verse2:
Kata In Ruodh polo, N' maler chutho,
To imor kiwinjo Wende nyithindi.
verse3:
Podi wan nyithindo, Waonge teko;
Yesu, wuothi kodwa, Kwaluwo yori.
verse4:
Igen'a e temruok, Iritwa pile;
Ket hera e chunywa, Golnwa kethrukwa.
verse5:
Chien'Yesu koluongowa Wanayie gi mor;
"Ee, Ruodhwa wabiro, Wanadhi kodi."

title: Yesu Ka Noa Malo
verse1:
Yesu ka noa polo mon'otho ni ji me piny,
Noparo e n'onone, Nyithindo ka wan.
verse2:
Mon nomanyo Jawarwa, Kwonde ka ma nopuonje;
Ne gikelo nyithindgi, Nyithindo ka wan.
verse3:
Yesu nobiro e piny, ni mon'owar jo molal;
Yesu e mokonyowa, Nyithindo ka wan.
verse4:
Nyithindo, hereuru, Ka utimo tich maber;
Pakeuru, Yesu Ruoth, To wan nyithinde.

title: Wan Nyithind Ruoth Yesu
verse2:
Wan wamako yor thurwa, Ka maber, ka maler;
Wan wamako yor thurwa, To wawer kwawuotho,
Wadhi dala mar Nyasaye Ka ma mudho onge chutho,
Nikech Yesu ni lerne; To wawer kwawuotho.

title: Luetega Noti Tich Mar Ruoth Yesu
verse1:
Luetega noti tich mar Ruoth Yesu, lewa bende nahulego;
Itega nowinj puonjne kende, Gi dwonda to napak Kristo.
verse2:
En nomiya tiendega ariyo, mondo awuoth e yo maber;
Wenge mabeyo ango bende, nasom Biblos ndalo duto.
verse3:
Kendo Yesu Kristo ma Jawarwa, odwaro chunya tinende;
Berna katimo tichne pile, ber kamiye ringra chutho.

title: Chon Nyithindo Nower Mamit
verse1:
Chon nyithindo nower wer mamit, Ka ne gipako Yesu Ruodh polo;
"Hosana, Hosana, Hosana e polo malo."
verse2:
Yesu pod ohero winjo wer, Koro kwapake, Yesu Ruodh Polo;
"Hosana, Hosana, Hosana e polo malo."
verse3:
Wabiro wero wer mamit chutho, gi jo mowar, eka wanamor ngan'
"Hosana, Hosana, Hosana e polo malo."

title: Ruodha Dak Imiya Tich
Winjuru Yuak Senti
verse1:
Winjuru yuak senti, Ka wabologi;
Duto gin mag Yesu, Mar konyo tichne.
verse2:
Ndalo mar Sabato to wakelo mich;
Ni osiepwa Yesu, En moherowa.
verse3:
Podi wan nyithindo, Mwandu ongenwa;
Kwadoko madongo Wanamedne mich.
verse4:
Kata pesa noknwa,Wachiwne hera;
Oyie mich mar chunywa, Kendo morgo chuth.

title: Nende Aluoko Lueta
verse1:
Nende aluoko lueta, Mondo gibed maler;
Kendo giti ni Yesu saa duto tinende.
verse2:
Ita ni mon'owinje E kinde duto te;
Abed gi chuny mar timo tich ma nyathi nyalo.
verse3:
Wan' mon'orit lueta kuom duto matimo;
Ni kik atim wach moro ma Yesu ok morgo.

title: Yesu Analu Bang'i
verse1:
Yesu analu ban', Asewinji kiluonga;
Adwaro mon'itelna, Inyisa wan'ori.
verse2:
Yesu, mak itelona, An abiro bayo yo;
Ok an'yo wan'ori, In mondo itelna.
verse3:
An kenda nanyap chutho, To di po kaol e yo;
An ageno tekoni, Adwaro itelna.

title: Yesu 'Hera Ang'eyo
verse2:
Yesu'era, ma notho mon'adonji e polo;
Enowena kethona, kendo miya chuny maler.
verse3:
Yesu'era, on'yo kakuyo kata katuo;
En Jakonya pile ka, orita ndalo duto.
verse4:
Yesu'era, En koda ndalo duto e piny ka;
Ka ahere nya'obi, chien'notera dalane.

title: Yesu 'Biro
verse1:
Yesu'iro, Yesu'iro, ni mon'ochok joge;
Joge duto, joge duto, moseyie nyinge.
verse2:
Enochokgi, enochokgi, Nyithinde malon';
Jo mabeyo, jo mabeyo, moseyie nyinge.
verse3:
Wan nyithinde, wan nyithinde, mohero Jawargi;
Enoomwa, enoomwa, wanadag kode.

title: Nyasaye Oneno Ka Winyo Odwaro Gore Piny
verse1:
Nyasaye oneno ka winyo odwaro gore piny;
Ka En ohero winyo cha, an'yo kohera.
verse2:
Thiepe duto manie e piny, Nyasaye nochweyogi;
Ka Nyasaye ohero thiepe, an'yo kohera.
verse3:
Nyasaye olosogi duto, kendo oritogi;
To an bende oparo an, an'yo kohera.

title: Ahero Ahinya Mar Chopo E Skul Mar Sabato
verse1:
Ahe'ahinya mar chopo, e skul mar Sabato;
Ahe'ahinya mar chopo, e skul mar Sabato.
verse2:
Ahe'ahinya mar wero, weche mag Ruoth Yesu;
Ahe'ahinya mar wero, e chien'mar Sabato.
verse3:
Ahe'ahinya mar chiwo, michna ni Ruoth Yesu;
Ahe'ahinya mar chiwo, e chien'mar Sabato.
verse4:
Ahe'ahinya mar lamo, Yesu Ruoth Jawarna;
Ahe'ahinya mar lamo e chien'mar Sabato.
verse5:
Ahe'ahinya mar n'yo, weche man kuom Yesu;
Ahero ahinya mar n'yo e chien'mar Sabato.

title: Nyasachwa Nochweyo Gik Moko Duto
verse1:
Nyasachwa nochweyo gik moko machon;
Ee, nochweyo duto kuom wachne kende.
verse2:
Yien, gi lum, gi chiembwa, rech man nie nam,
Winy duto mafuyo, En nochweyogi.
verse3:
Chien'machiwo lerne odiechien'pile;
Sulwe to gi dwe be marieny gotieno.
verse4:
Dhano'oyo duto manochweyo chon;
En onyalo hingo wach Nyasaye adier.

title: Pakeuru ,Un Nyithindo
verse1:
Pakeuru, un nyithindo duto, En hera, En hera;
Pakeuru, un nyithindo duto, En hera, En hera.
verse2:
Hereuru un nyithindo duto, En hera, En hera;
Hereuru, un nyithindo duto, En hera, En hera.
verse3:
Luweuru, un nyithindo duto, En hera, En hera;
Luweuru, un nyithindo duto, En hera, En hera.
verse4:
Un nyithindo, ruak Yesu e chunyu, En hera, En hera;
Un nyithindo, ruak Yesu e chunyu, En hera, En hera.

title: Bedo Gi Yesu E Dala Mano Maduong
verse1:
Bedo gi Yesu e dala, mano mor maduon'
Mano mor maduon' mano mor maduon'
Bedo gi Yesu e dala, mano mor maduon'
Mano mor maduon'
verse2:
Ka Yesu ni e chuny wuoro, ot bedo mokuwe,
Ot bedo mokuwe, ot bedo mokuwe;
Ka Yesu ni e chuny wuoro, ot bedo mokuwe,
Ot bedo mokuwe.
verse3:
Ka Yesu ni e chuny miyo, ot bedo mokuwe, 
Ot bedo mokuwe, ot bedo mokuwe;
Ka Yesu ni e chuny miyo, ot bedo mokuwe,
Ot bedo mokuwe.
verse4:
Yesu e chuny nyithindo, ot bedo mokuwe,
Ot bedo mokuwe, ot bedo mokuwe;
Yesu e chuny nyithindo, ot bedo mokuwe,
Ot bedo mokuwe.

title: Nogola E Bugo
verse1:
Ne litna ka richona nokelo tho,
Kendo kanaywak e bugo mar richo;
Ruoth nowinja gi e bugo matutno,
Modemba, ogola, moketa e mor.
verse2:
Noketa ewi Lwanda bute chutho,
Nosira motegno mon'asik kanyo;
Ok naluor podho kasiko e lwete,
Nagen kuom n'onone nyaka ayud locho.
verse3:
Nomiya wer mamit ne en wer mar pak,
Odiechien'gotieno anawer wendno;
Chunya nigi ilo amor an thuolo,
Anapak Jawarna ma oseresa.
verse4:
Anawer n'onone miwuoro kuoma,
Anapake nyaka jii none berne;
Anawer wend warruok kuonde duto te,
Nyaka ji man'ny noyie kuom Nyasaye.

title: Yiengni kuom Ruoth Yesu
verse1:
Yiengri mana kuom Ruodhwa Yesu,
En nokonyi ka, nokonyi ka;
Ka in gi geno kuome chutho,
Chunyi nobed gi mor.
verse2:
Yiengri mana kuom Ruodhwa Yesu,
Enomenyi yori, nomeny yori;
Luwe gi mor ka oteloni,
Dwonde mon'iwiinji.
verse3:
Yiengri mana kuom Ruodhwa Yesu,
Kikelo chandruokni, chandruok duto;
Mago mapek machando chunyi,
Ketgi ni Ruoth Yesu.
verse4:
Yiengri mana kuom Ruodhwa Yesu,
We duto kuome, duto kuome;
Chuny ma en go opon'kod n'ono,
Wan' en mar hera.

title: Nitie Kamaber Mar Yweyo
verse1:
Nitie kamaber mar yweyo machiegni gi Nyasaye;
Kama richo ok nyal donje, machiegni gi Nyasaye.
verse2:
Nitie kanyo maber mar hoch, machiegni gi Nyasaye;
Kama waro'e gi Jawar, machiegni gi Nyasaye.
verse3:
Kanyo ji duto ni thuolo, machiegni gi Nyasaye,
En kama mor gi kwe nitie, machiegni gi Nyasaye.

title: Ruoth Nyasacha
verse1:
Ruoth Nyasacha, aneno gik miwuoro,
Miseketo e pinyni mwadakie;
Wan'chien'gi due, gi sulwe man e polo,
Gik moko te ma lueti noloso.
verse2:
Ka awuotho e bunge to awinjo,
Winy mapaki gi duonde miwuoro;
Ka abedo e gode mabor chutho,
Awinjo duonde mag pige mamol.
verse3:
Kaparo ni Nyasaye  nochiwo Wuode,
Mondo otho en wach miwuoro ngan'
E wi yadhno notin' kethna duto,
Rembe nochwer moluoko richona.
verse4:
Ka Kristo nobi gi teko gi duon'e,
Nadhi kode nobed mor manade;
Nakulra e nyime ka amiye duon'
Kawacho ni In Nyasacha Maduon'

title: Chungo E Singo Mar Nyasaye
verse1:
Chungo e singono mar Ruodhwa Yesu,
Tienge duto mon'owinj pak mare;
Anakogi kawero duon'mar polo,
Kachungo e singo mar Nyasaye.
verse2:
Chungo e singono ma ok nyal rem ngan'
Ka yembe mag kiawa kod luoro kudho;
To gi wach Nyasaye ok nyal podho,
Kachungo e singono mar Nyasaye.

title: Wachiegni Dhi Dala
verse1:
Waweruru wer mamiyowa mor e yo,
Machiegni wanadhi dalawa;
Mudho norum chuth chien'o ma Ruodhwa nobi,
Machiegni wanadhi dalawa.
verse2:
Watimuru tich gi getokowa duto te,
Machiegni wanadhi dalawa;
To n'ono Nyasaye nomiwa teko pile,
Machiegni wanadhi dalawa.
verse3:
Walosuru yo ni tiende duto mool,
Machiegni wanadhi dalawa;
To chuny mar hera oywa joma ni butwa,
Machiegni wanadhi dalawa.
verse4:
Wanaywe kanyo ok wanabed gi parruok,
Machiegni wanadhi dalawa;
Dalano ma rieny pi wan'ok nochwerie ngan'
Machiegni wanadhi dalawa.

title: Ruodha Telna
verse1:
Ruodha telna kuom kuyo moluora,
Med telona, mudho olil an mabor gi dala;
Med telona ok anyal neno mabor moloyo,
Yie itelna mondo alu ban'.

title: In Koso An
verse1:
N'to nodonj e ranga lulu e chien'o,
E chien'o mon'one duon'o maritowa.
In koso an? In koso an?
N't ma nolu yo mar dhahabu,
Nenruok malich mobedo kanyo,
Donjo e morno mwasewinjo;
In koso an? In Koso an?
verse2:
N't ma nomor ka oselocho, e chien'o,
E chien'o, noyud osimbo kod pak kuom Ruoth;
In koso an? In koso an?
N't manone Ruodhwa man gi duon'
Ka oseloyo kuyo mar piny,
Enobed mamor manyaka chien'
In Koso an? In koso an?
verse3:
N't manower wendno mar locho, e chien'o,
E chien'o, noriwre e wend jomosewar;
In koso an? In koso an?
N't manochun'e dho nam ran',
Nomosre kod osiepe mowar,
Nobed e duon'o manyaka chien'
In koso an? In koso an?

title: Yesu Kristo Osechier
verse1:
Yesu Kristo osechier, Alleluya!
Dhano, Malaika wer, Alleluya!
Wer mar mor kod wend locho, Alleluya!
Polo wer be piny duoko, Alleluya!
verse2:
Ruoth Maduon'ngima koro, Alleluya!
Ere lit ma tho kelo? Alleluya!
Ne otho mon'owarwa, Alleluya!
Ere loch ma liel nigo? Alleluya!
verse3:
Hera okelo warruok, Alleluya!
Oseloyo lweny mager, Alleluya!
Tho to ok nyal gen' ngan' Alleluya!
Kristo oseyaw kar dak, Alleluyah!
verse4:
Wanalu ndach Ruoth Yesu, Alleluya!
Kawadhi ban'Jatendwa, Alleluya!
Kwasedoko kaka En, Alleluya!
Msalaba, liel, polo, Alleluya!

title: Kik chunyi a ka'e chandruok
verse1:
Kik chunyi a ka'e chandruok, Nyasaye mon'oriti,
E bwo bwombe kod herane, Nyasaye mon'oriti.
verse2:
Ka chunyi ol nikech chandruok, Nyasaye mon'oriti,
Ka masiche pon' yori, Nyasaye mon'oriti.
verse3:
Dwaroni duto Enolo, Nyasaye mon'oriti,
Gene ni mondo okonyi, Nyasaye mon'oriti.

title: Yie Mar Kwerewa
verse1:
Yie mar kwerewa pod nitie ban'loyo twech, sand kod mach be;
Chunywa opon'gi mor chutho kawawinjo wachni maber.
verse2:
Twech mar kwerewa e mudho ne ok oketho yie margi;
Dibed maber ni nyithindgi ka gin bende giyie kuome.
verse3:
Yie mar kwerewa wanaher osiepe, wasigu bende;
Kendo wanalandi gi hera kod weche man'on mag ngima.

title: Ywaya Iri Ruoth
verse1:
Ywaya iri, iri, iri, Ruoth maber,
E msalaba kar thoni;
Ywaya iri, iri, iri, Ruoth maber,
Nyaka abed mari chutho.

title: Ok An Kenda Ngang
verse1: Ka Yesu ni koda ok an kenda ngang';
verse2: Kat' osiepe weya to En Osiepna;
verse3: To kata otera e yore malich,
verse4: Ka Yesu ni koda to nabed mamor.

title: E Chunya Awinjo Wer Mamit
verse1: E chunya awinjo wer mamit,
verse2: Awinjo wer mamit
verse3: Machal gi wend polo;
verse4: E chunya awinjo wer mamit,
verse5: Awinjo wend hera mamit.

title: Yesu, Yesu, Yesu
verse1: Kneels at the feet of his friends;
verse2: Silently washes their feet,
verse3: Master who acts as a slave to them.
refrain: Yesu, Yesu, fill us with your love, show us how to serve the neighbors we have from you.

title: Luwo, Luwo, Analu Bang' Yesu
verse1: Luwo, luwo, analu bang' Yesu;
verse2: Kata ka, kata ku, analu bang'e;
verse3: Luwo, luwo, analu bang' Yesu;
verse4: Kwonde duto motelona analu.

title: Anatimu Joyuwa Ji
verse2:
Ka ulu bang'a,
Ka ulu bang'a;
Anatimu joyuwa ji,
Ka ulu bang'a.

title: An Achamo Kuon Mar Ngima Adier
verse1:
An achamo kuon mar ngima adier,
Kwom ruodhwa Yesu,
Anuommo e kor mar ngima,
Nying' Yesu marach.
verse2:
Chalo manie gi wang' yien,
Kuon ngima ma okel,
An achamo e ngeyo,
Bende ni Yesu marach.
verse3:
Koro kaluwore koro,
To Yesu ni tich,
Chalo manie mar adier,
Nying' Yesu marach.
verse4:
Koro romo otho chendo,
Ang'o wuon Yesu,
Nying' Yesu, joma okeli,
Nying' Yesu marach.
refrain:
Nying' Yesu marach!
Mar ngima, mar ngima,
Ngima ma adier,
Nying' Yesu marach.

title: E Chunya E Chunya
Piny Duto Dwaro Yesu
verse1:
Piny duto dwaro Yesu,
Gidwaro nene,
Piny duto dwaro Yesu,
Gidwaro nene;
verse2:
Nomi ji mor maduong` ngang,
Nogol richo gi kuyo;
Piny duto dwaro Yesu,
Gidwaro nene.

title: Nyasaye Gotienoni
verse1:
Nyasaye gotienoni,
Mondo irtiwa ngang`;
Mondo kik gimoro chamwa,
Nyaka iyawnwa piny.
verse2: Amin!

title: Ruoth Kwagoni Chongwa Piny
verse1:
Ruoth, kwagoni chongwa piny ka,
Gwedhwa te ka pok wake;
verse2:
Pwodhwa, gudwa, luokwa chutho,
Bi, dak e chunywa duto.

title: Wabiro Neno Ruodhwa
verse1:
Wabiro neno Ruodhwa,
Wabiro neno Ruodhwa,
Wabiro neno Ruodhwa,
Kobiro kod duong`ne;
verse2:
Eka nosidhne osimbo,
Eka nosidhne osimbo,
Eka nosidhne osimbo,
Mondo obed Ruodh ji duto.

title: Wanga E Maneno Nyasaye
verse1:
Wang'a e maneno Nyasaye,
Ita e mawinjo Wachne;
verse2:
Tienda e mawuotho e yorene,
Dhoga e mapako duong`ne;
verse3:
Lueta e matiyo tichne,
Chunya e maherego pile.

title: Mor Mor Mor
verse1:
Mor, mor, mor,
E chunya sani;
Yesu dwoko dwarana,
Mor sani.
verse2:
Mor, mor, mor,
Yesu ruodha sani;
Dwoko chunya marach sani,
Mor sani.
verse3:
Mor, mor, mor,
Pile e chunya sani;
Yesu okel mor maduongʼ,
E chunya.
